<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no" ?>
<FinalDraft DocumentType="Script" Template="No" Version="1">

  <Content>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="1" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="6/8" Page="1" Title="The Past is Prologe"/>
      <Text>EXT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - PARKING AREA - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="39" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="40" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="43" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="44" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="7" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="45" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="46" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="47" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="0" ElementID="48" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">Text: </Text>
      <Text>201</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">7</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES 35, a sexy young woman, looks shocked. The gunman shoots her in the chest. TARA REED 33, SHAWNTEY ROSS 34 and CASSIDY REDMAN 34 all take a step back shook by this turn of events. Tara tosses the keys to the lead masked man. He grabs them out of the air and quickly moves to the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. He starts it and pulls off. The remaining gunmen slowly move to a cargo van, one jumps in the driver’s seat. The other stands in front of the side sliding door and pulls the slide on his assault rifle, chambering a round. Shawntey looks to Tara they both know what’s coming. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="89" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="2" ElementID="2" SceneID="0" Start="89" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="2" ElementID="13" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="13"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="124" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="2" ElementID="16" SceneID="0" Start="124" Length="14"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="363" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="2" ElementID="41" SceneID="0" Start="363" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="209" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="2" ElementID="42" SceneID="0" Start="209" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION, Tara has a look of peace, Shawntey looks panicked. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="4" ElementID="1" SceneID="0" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tara, I.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Obscured by a parked car, only the gunmen that aims at Tara and her crew can be seen. He let’s out a blast of gun fire. He then jumps into the awaiting van and it pulls away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>OVER BLACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(phrase overlapping randomly, repeating at different levels) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>They will all pay. Betrayed us! Betrayed me! But how and who? I’m going to find you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="2" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="3/8" Page="1" Title="Shows Shawntey's frustration">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">This shows Shawntey's frustration. This is the space that he is tempted by Tara's offer and the reemergance of Mr. Diaz.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""/>
          </Paragraph>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey is bubbling anger/frustration</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. SHAWNTEY ROSS’S FORD DEALERSHIP - daY</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="12" ElementID="1" SceneID="12" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">Text: 2008</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey sits behind his desk in his Ford dealership which isn’t in good financial condition. There are no sales and a never-ending string of bills and debt that have him on edge. His secretary brings in more of the same. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Was it as close as my right hand... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey looks up to the secretary with a mean face as she leaves. He looks down to the paperwork and slowly he works himself into an explosion. He throws the paperwork then wipes the desk of everything. THE FRAME FREEZES with Shawntey’s face contorted in anger. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="25" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="18" ElementID="49" SceneID="12" Start="25" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="88" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="18" ElementID="50" SceneID="12" Start="88" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="3" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="3/8" Page="2" Title="No Worries">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Mr. Diaz has/shows no worries. He doesn't have a care. Hw walks in between the rain drops and can't be out thought/planned</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. VICENTES CUBAN CUISINE - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="19" ElementID="8" SceneID="19" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON AN ASH TRAY a cigar smolders with a beer glass half filled next to it. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="12" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="21" ElementID="51" SceneID="19" Start="12" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="21" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="21" ElementID="52" SceneID="19" Start="21" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION a hand picks up the cigar. The arm has beautiful cuff links on the sleeve and a Role Presidential on the wrist. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="54" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="22" ElementID="53" SceneID="19" Start="54" Length="20"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="93" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="22" ElementID="54" SceneID="19" Start="93" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON A MAN’S LIPS. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The man takes a drag. The sits in this restaurant alone, his identity hide my the white hat that he wears. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="82" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="24" ElementID="55" SceneID="19" Start="82" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>...Or a partner </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="4" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="5/8" Page="2" Title="A Nasty Dude">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Vincent gives off the air of shady. He gives a grimmyy feel/smile. He always knows more than you.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. EAST-SIDE CAR WASH - OFFICE - night</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="27" ElementID="52" SceneID="27" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON VINCENT 45. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="29" ElementID="23" SceneID="27" Start="9" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION, THE SHOT pulls back from him as he poses. The big cloud of smoke that he puffs up begins to obscures him. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="20" CategoryID="14" ParagraphID="30" ElementID="56" SceneID="27" Start="20" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>...Or was it the hate that hate  made. How to get them to show themselves? Got to find a way. I’m glad I thought ahead enough to get the insurance in place. But who can I trust? (a beat) On wrongs, swift vengeance awaits! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>WHITE TEXT OVER BLACK SCREEN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>“Patience serves as a protection against wrongs as clothes do against cold...” </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">TEXT: </Text>
      <Text>LEONARD  Da VINCE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE IN: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text/>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">TEXT: </Text>
      <Text>THE VIRTUE OF PATIENCE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="5" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1 6/8" Page="2" Title="Marco gloats">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">The game has been played, Marco is being questioned. He doesn't know anything because he's been in jail, to them. But when time freezes, Marco has played his hand and all have paid for their sins. He gloats, he's beat them all!</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. FBI TASK-FORCE OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="14" ParagraphID="40" ElementID="64" SceneID="40" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="14" ParagraphID="40" ElementID="56" SceneID="40" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">Text: Present</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Quick cuts of black and white surveillance photos. Tara standing outside of the Reed Holdings offices talking to Xiomare. Grease pencil marks tell the names of the people in the photos. Arrows point to their connection to each other. A photo of Shawntey talking on his cell sitting in a black SUV. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="14" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="42" ElementID="57" SceneID="40" Start="14" Length="35"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A photo of the ladies moving inside of a bank carrying briefcases and duffle bags. A photo with MR. DIAZ 50 and TINY 34 is penned on this board as well. Mr. Diaz is circled in red grease pencil with arrows pointing inward to him. The pictures are penned to a cork board in this warehouse. Gliding down the isle of this warehouse turned headquarters. There are FBI AGENTS scurrying in every direction. Desks line both sides of the walk way. Several agents talk on phone calls, some at computers, all very intent in their movements. At the end of this walkway is MARCO REED SR 34. He sits at the side of a desk, his elbows on his knees, his head down. There re several agents standing over him, one sitting on the desk that he sits at. Marco is definitely the center of attention. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="360" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="43" ElementID="58" SceneID="40" Start="360" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="476" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="43" ElementID="59" SceneID="40" Start="476" Length="17"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="561" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="43" ElementID="60" SceneID="40" Start="561" Length="13"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="257" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="43" ElementID="61" SceneID="40" Start="257" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="463" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="43" ElementID="62" SceneID="40" Start="463" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The sound of the questions gets louder. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>FBI AGENT 1 (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>...Four dead cops convict, your * wife and all her friends in the middle of this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text/>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON DIGITAL RECORDER, one of the FBI agents hits the play button. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="48" ElementID="63" SceneID="40" Start="9" Length="16"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (TAPED) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>...after, we can melt into any background you want. Trust me T, </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll make this right. Just like we talked about. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (TAPED) </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="52" ElementID="2" SceneID="40" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m not sure that person is inside me Marco. What if I can’t do this, then what? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The FBI agent pushes the stop button and the questions continue. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>FBI AGENT 1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="55" ElementID="3" SceneID="40" Start="0" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What background? Where is your wife?? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>FBI AGENT 2 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="57" ElementID="4" SceneID="40" Start="0" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Who’s the person she needed to be for you Marco? You ask her to be a killer? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>FBI Agent 1 tries another tact, a softer tone. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>FBI AGENT 1 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Come on man, think about your son. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We want to help your family. Tell me something... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The voices fade out, the sounds of the room fade away. The office freezes in time. All things freeze wherever they are. There’s an agent that’s pouring a cup of coffee, it too freezes in place. Marco has not frozen in this time vacuum. He lifts his head, his eyes find the LENS. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="64" ElementID="5" SceneID="40" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ve been looking back at my choices. The important thing was to make sure we’d thought of everything, considered every move. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>My thoughts race over every conversation that I've had over the course of the last three years, including this one.  I’ve lost ALMOST everything. But it wasn’t without help. Somebody close to me betrayed us. I'm Marco Reed Sr inmate #35728, or at least I was until a couple of hours ago. I think I'm the only person that goes from prison to the FBI office. I’m here, and they’re doing their FBI thing, asking the questions. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>He rub his head with his hand. The background changes around him, as though it is falling away revealing the new background. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="6" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 1/8" Page="4" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. PRISON VISITOR'S ROOM - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="68" ElementID="38" SceneID="68" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="68" ElementID="66" SceneID="68" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="68" ElementID="68" SceneID="68" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">TEXT: </Text>
      <Text>200</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">8</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco sits in front of the visitor’s glass, looking very upset. A man sits in front of him. His face can’t be seen. A big onyx ring on his pinky finger distinguishes him. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="116" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="70" ElementID="65" SceneID="68" Start="116" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNSEEN MAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="71" ElementID="292" SceneID="68" Start="0" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Are you sure you want to do this? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Eight years for conspiracy is a gift. You only going to do five or six. Do the time and walk away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="74" ElementID="5" SceneID="68" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Gift! You want to trade </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> places? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco sits back, thinking.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (V.O.) (CONT’D)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It was like a couple months after I landed inside. A business associate came to see me. He told me that a snitch put the FBI on us. This business brings all kinds of enemies and bed fellows. At a price though, someone like me can do business with almost anybody. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Assault weapons in house, in front of my kid! I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">want’em</Text>
      <Text> all. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNSEEN MAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It ain’t going to be easy and very expensive. He’s not going to show himself to me or anyone else we know. I’m not sure we can get him to step into the open. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A small smile spread across Marco’s face.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea, he’ll come to us and the rest of them too. I got insurance. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text/>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>UNSEEN MAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(chuckles) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Insurance? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(nodding) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No worries, can you do the rest? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">The Unseen Man slides a hundred dollar bill into the hand of the CO as he walks out.</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="22" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="93" ElementID="67" SceneID="68" Start="22" Length="21"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="7" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="5" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. FBI TASK-FORCE OFFICE - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>PRESENT </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">TEXT: </Text>
      <Text>2011 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Time is still frozen. Marco looks directly into CAMERA. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="97" ElementID="5" SceneID="94" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">got’em</Text>
      <Text> all!. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="8" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1 7/8" Page="6" Title="The Game Begins... Tara struggles!">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara is struggling with the road ahead. She waivers for a bit, but is back in the fold by the end. This is Tara not sure of herself at the end so we show how far she goes by the end.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT.  PRISON VISITOR'S ROOM - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="100" ElementID="69" SceneID="100" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK: </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">TEXT: </Text>
      <Text>2006 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco has the phone to speak to visitors in his hand; </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="103" ElementID="5" SceneID="100" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">...after</Text>
      <Text>, we can melt into any background you want. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>When the words leave his lips Marco knows that they will have no impact. After the police chases, and confiscation of her life and the trial, the tears and words for that matter are gone. Tara, Marco’s wife, sits in front of him. Her hair in a ponytail that’s showing some strain. She has their young son, MARCO REED JR 5 on her lap. Tara has the intercom phone in her hand listening to Marco, her eyes down. Marco tries more words. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(starts to speak, then )</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(stops) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Trust me T, I’ll make this right. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(raises his eyebrows) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Just like we talked about. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara shakes her head, she was wavering but something brings her back. She pulls it back together. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="113" ElementID="2" SceneID="100" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m not sure that person is inside me Marco. What if I can’t do this, then what? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco sits back in his seat and lets out a sigh. He realizes that this may be to much for Tara. Though he knows nothing is beyond her. He then leans back into her. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Maybe we should wait. I can..... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No, no. I’m going to do this, </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(more solidly) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I want to do this. I got to start back before it gets to late. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(talking to Marco Jr.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Say bye to your daddy. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hands Marco Jr the phone. Marco Jr takes the phone into his little hand. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO JR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="126" ElementID="7" SceneID="100" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Bye daddy. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Bye baby, listen to your mother. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll be home soon. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hangs up the phone and collects Marco Jr’s stuff. Marco Sr knocks on the glass with his phone. Tara turns. Marco speaks through the glass. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Congrats</Text>
      <Text> baby, its a big deal. I wish I could have came to the ceremony and seen you in the dress or gown or what they call it. It’ll help you, help us. Use it! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco looks back towards the guard behind him, then back to Tara. Tara thoughts have race totally to a different place and she can’t figure what Marco is talking about. She picks up the phone again. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Walking across the stage. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Graduation. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara realizes finally what he’s talking about. The first semblance of a smile shows on her face. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Oh that reminds me, I brought you a picture. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sits the phone down and grabs her purse and takes out a picture of her walking across the stage. She smiles but it seems forced. Tara sits down and holds the picture to the glass and picks up the phone. Marco looks at the picture with a huge smile. He clearly loves his wife. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="59" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="143" ElementID="70" SceneID="100" Start="59" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll leave it for you in the front. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(smiles)  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Got to go baby. Love you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hangs up the phone, kisses her hand and touches the glass. Marco does the same. Tara takes little Marco and leaves the room. Marco remains seated. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="9" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="2/8" Page="7" Title="How Far Tara has stepped back.">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Here we show that Tara doesn't have the hot car and what goes with that... The easy life etc. It maybe should be a little hard to belt Lil Marco in or something to drive home its not easy no more. And she was robbed of that. Maybe a little fristration here with not getting the seat belt in, or it's broken.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. PRISON PARKING AREA - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="149" ElementID="2" SceneID="149" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="149" ElementID="7" SceneID="149" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="149" ElementID="71" SceneID="149" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="149" ElementID="72" SceneID="149" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="14" ParagraphID="149" ElementID="73" SceneID="149" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>TITLES BEGIN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara walks to her modest car. She straps Marco Jr into the back seat, then gets in. She takes a beat to gather herself from the drama behind her and prepares for the road ahead. Tara pulls out of the visitors parking lot. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="10" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="2/8" Page="8" Title="Sets Tara's right now.">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">We look around how Tara is making it happen now. We see the pictures of her &quot;Mansion Life&quot; and its contrasted against this very modest apartment. We see the degree to illustrate that she has the brains to pull this off.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> FRONT ROOM</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Several quick shots of the modest apartment, starting with the family pictures. The pictures show better times. The house, the cars, the smiles illustrate the level of success they live with. On that same mantle, Tara’s degree in finance from University of </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Loyola</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Marymont</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="63" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="154" ElementID="74" SceneID="153" Start="63" Length="15"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="213" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="154" ElementID="75" SceneID="153" Start="213" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="11" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="2/8" Page="8" Title="Tara's Financial Push...">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Here we don't know that Tara and Marco has such a deep thing planned. So her she plays the role of pressed. She looks thru the digital want-ads, just after the rescession has lifted but the jobs haven't come back. She's frustrated.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>KITCHEN AREA - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="155" ElementID="2" SceneID="155" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="14" ParagraphID="155" ElementID="77" SceneID="155" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sits at the kitchen table on her computer looking at job openings on the Career Builder web site. She’s looking frustrated at the options. There’s a knock on the door. She looks up from her paper, not expecting anyone. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="38" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="156" ElementID="76" SceneID="155" Start="38" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara eases the paper down and moves to the door. The paper’s headline, “RECESSION DEEPENS, JOBLESS NUMBER AT 25 YEAR HIGH” </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="12" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="2/8" Page="8" Title="TARA NOT SURE">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara is not sure if this is thre beginning. She looks and looks again. Is this the guy?</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>DOOR AREA - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara arrives at the door and eases the chain on the door, then looks out of the peephole. She thinks for a beat, then looks again. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="160" ElementID="2" SceneID="158" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea, who is it? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="13" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="3/8" Page="8" Title="Danger In A Man">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Mr. Diaz stands on the other side shaped as danger/opportunity. He nevertheless is sure of himself and his moves. He still worries not about the triffles of men!</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>HALLWAY - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz a well dressed man along with Tiny, a very large African-American man stand in the hallway. Mr. Diaz steps forward to the door. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="39" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="163" ElementID="78" SceneID="162" Start="39" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="164" ElementID="8" SceneID="162" Start="0" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(thick Spanish accent) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hello Mrs. Reed. I’m Mr. Diaz and this is my associate Tiny. I’m a </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(corrects himself) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">was</Text>
      <Text> a business partner of your husband’s and I have something for you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz smiles, trying to be as non-threatening as possible. Tara isn’t moved. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="14" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="3/8" Page="9" Title="TARA Thinks About The Crew">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Here mentally introduces everyone in the crew. She flash to why tyhey all would be down. It's her checking in with everyone mentally and are they in a space to let this danger in and start the plan.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT.  </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>DOOR AREA - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="170" ElementID="2" SceneID="170" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara continues to look through the peephole. Mr. Diaz tries again, this time not with as much charm. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      </UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tara, my associate Tiny is going to have to kick in the door if you don't open it. I don't want him to have do that but this business won't wait. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara thinks for a beat, just looking out of the peephole. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="15" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1 3/8" Page="9" Title="Kim's Motivation">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kim realizes the price of her upward mobility. She does want to pay this price because its not on her terms. She isees the guy and is revolted by it. This is her motivation.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT.  CHASE SECURITIES MANAGEMENT - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>There are several family pictures around this modest office. A degree from </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Loyola</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Marymont</Text>
      <Text> in finance is framed in silver along side a MBA from the same. KIM PEREZ 32 sits at her desk. She’s intently pouring over her market charts and trends, both in front of her on the desk as well as on her computer screen. A knock on her door brings her out of her trance. At the door is GARY KLINE 55, the senior market analysis, Kim’s boss. Kim looks up to see it’s him and just as quickly returns her attention to her work. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="18" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="176" ElementID="74" SceneID="175" Start="18" Length="15"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="63" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="176" ElementID="79" SceneID="175" Start="63" Length="27"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="217" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="176" ElementID="80" SceneID="175" Start="217" Length="13"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="294" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="176" ElementID="76" SceneID="175" Start="294" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>KIM PEREZ </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="177" ElementID="9" SceneID="175" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What do you need Gary? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>GARY KLEIN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="179" ElementID="10" SceneID="175" Start="0" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Oooh</Text>
      <Text>, what </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">kinda</Text>
      <Text> tone is that this early in the morning? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Gary strolls into the office and sits on the corner of Kim’s desk. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>GARY KLEIN (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I got a bit of bad news. They promoted Rick Kim. But, I think they’ll have another analysis position coming open next quarter. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Everyone in this market is scared to death. Anyone that can see the future is going to be worth their weight in gold. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim does a double take, looking up to Gary as he continues. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>GARY KLEIN (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I tell you what though, I have my analysis and management retreat in  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tahoe. The spa is unbelievable. Besides all the promotion seem to come from my meetings. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE-UP ON GARY’S EYES, he’s not looking at Kim’s face, but at her chest. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE-UP OF GARY LICKING HIS LIPS, almost like the wolf looking at the lamb. Kim’s brow furrows taking in his non- verbal advances. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>GARY KLEIN (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You should think about it. I’m almost sure if you CAME a few times, I could get you a serious look for that next analysis slot. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Gary’s face turns back to that of a co-worker, from the beast of preys. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>GARY KLEIN (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Anyway, give it some thought. I’ll be around. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Gary moves to door to leave. He speaks over his shoulder. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>GARY KLEIN (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Have a great day sweetheart. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim throws her pencil at the door. This is the last straw. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="16" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1" Page="10" Title="Cassidy's motivation.">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">With her skilll set its hard to see moeny, espercially the money that is involved. This is her motivation, at first. Frustration for Cassidy.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">GTS</Text>
      <Text> UNLIMITED FIREARMS RANGE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="201" ElementID="87" SceneID="201" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="201" ElementID="44" SceneID="201" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON THE STRAINED EXPRESSION of Cassidy, a brown skin beauty. Her exotic beauty mask the fury that lies just below. Cassidy is an Iraq war vet, a army ranger retire now after 8 years of services. She’s wearing noise muffling headphones, and shooting glasses. The noise of gunfire rings out. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="245" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="202" ElementID="85" SceneID="201" Start="245" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="214" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="202" ElementID="86" SceneID="201" Start="214" Length="25"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy is standing next to MRS. MICHAELS 62. They’re the only two on the range. A man carrying a clip board wearing a set of muffling headphones and shooting glasses approaches unseen to Cassidy. He taps her on the shoulder for her to take off her headphones. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>GUN RANGE MANAGER </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="204" ElementID="11" SceneID="201" Start="0" Length="17"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re going to have to cut your hours next week. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy looks the man in his face. He screams more into her ear as Mrs. Michaels continues firing. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>GUN RANGE MANAGER (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m sorry but we’re just not getting the bookings. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The manager hands her an envelope off the clipboard. He has Cassidy sign for it. Cassidy turns to watch the manager walk away as she opens the envelope. She looks down at the contents. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="4" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="209" ElementID="81" SceneID="201" Start="4" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="22" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="209" ElementID="82" SceneID="201" Start="22" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="42" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="209" ElementID="83" SceneID="201" Start="42" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON THE CHECK FOR $302 </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="210" ElementID="84" SceneID="201" Start="9" Length="18"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy’s face shows the strain at once, she balls the envelope up and smashes it into her pocket. Her strain deepens as Mrs. Michaels adds to the misfortune. She stops shooting and pulls down her headphones </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MRS. MICHAELS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="212" ElementID="12" SceneID="201" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cassidy I don’t think I’ll be able to make it next week, in fact I think this is my last time. My husband doesn’t think... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy’s strain is at it’s highest. Mrs. Michael’s voice fades out as she continues to explain. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="17" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="5/8" Page="11" Title="Xiomare's Motivation">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare wants to be from under everyone. She's tired of the men not being there. She sees the prize and goes for it. Here she is just frustrated.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">MAGGIE’S</Text>
      <Text> HEADS - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="216" ElementID="88" SceneID="216" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="216" ElementID="89" SceneID="216" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="216" ElementID="90" SceneID="216" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare is Tara’s best friend. A sexy young woman always on the make. She has found that she can move people to do things for her by using her ample sexual prowess. She’s doing her client’s hair at this crowded beauty shop. Xiomare is dress to attract, her voluptuous body calls everyone’s attention, men and women. Her cell rings. She looks at it, then twist her lips knowing that there’s drama on the other end. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="218" ElementID="13" SceneID="216" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea? What you mean you can’t make it? You’re just trifling dude. A sorry excuse for a man. Don’t worry about my baby I’ll do it myself. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(ends call) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shit</Text>
      <Text>! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare leans in to her client. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Faith I’m sorry but I got to go get my son and take him to day-care. His sorry as daddy can’t do </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The client in the chair doesn’t get a chance to protest. Xiomare has her smock off and is heading for the door before she can get a word out. Xiomare storms out of the beauty shop. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="18" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1/8" Page="12" Title="Tara stands at the crossroads">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara stands at the crossroads. This moment decides it all!</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT - FRONT DOOR </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">- DAY</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="227" ElementID="2" SceneID="227" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara still at the door looking through the peephole. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="19" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="2/8" Page="12" Title="Mr. Diaz Insisst">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Mr. Diaz steps back and insist that Tony opens the door.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>HALLWAY - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="229" ElementID="78" SceneID="229" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz steps back from the door and Tiny steps forward. A few beats more and Tiny looks to Mr. Diaz for the signal to kick it in. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="230" ElementID="8" SceneID="229" Start="0" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="20" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1 1/8" Page="12" Title="TARA GIVE IN AND LETS MR. DIAZ IN">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">tara let's Mr. Diaz in and Tiiny scans for microphones.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>DOOR AREA - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="231" ElementID="78" SceneID="231" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara opens the door with the chain on. When Tara opens the door she can see the two large suitcases that Tiny has at his feet. She closes the door again to take the chain off. She opens the door and Tiny steps right in. Mr. Diaz stays in the hallway. Tara watches as Tiny pulls out what looks like a radio receiver of some sort and begins to scan the apartment starting with Tara. She holds the door in her hand as she watches, half amazed at the circumstance. Tiny moves into the bedrooms. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="220" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="232" ElementID="8" SceneID="231" Start="220" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="298" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="232" ElementID="91" SceneID="231" Start="298" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="80" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="232" ElementID="92" SceneID="231" Start="80" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="233" ElementID="2" SceneID="231" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey dude you can’t go in... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Before she can finish the sentence Tiny comes out. He nods to Mr. Diaz. Mr, Diaz looks down the hallway both ways then steps into the apartment. Tara closing the door behind him. He takes off his hat. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You can never be to careful. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(reaches out to shake )</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(Tara’s hand) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m Mr. Diaz, a former business partner of your husband. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara shakes his hand, still on guard. She looks back to Tiny, who still hasn’t said a word. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>If you were partners with Marco you know that he’s not home. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yes of course Mrs. Reed. That's </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">kinda</Text>
      <Text> why I’m here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz strolls around the apartment. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Can I trouble you for a glass of water or juice something? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara still not at all at ease. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ah, yea sure. I got cranberry juice or water? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara moves to the kitchen to get the drink. Mr. Diaz follows as he decides. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cranberry would be great. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="21" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1" Page="13" Title="MR. DIAZ LAYS OUT THE INSURANCE TO TARA.">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">mr. Diaz tells Tara that Marco made these arrangements. She plays it as if she doesn't know anything. But clearly she has lured the mystical Mr. Diaz out in the open.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>KITCHEN AREA - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="323" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="255" ElementID="78" SceneID="255" Start="323" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="255" ElementID="92" SceneID="255" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="255" ElementID="93" SceneID="255" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara grabs a glass and then the juice from the fig. She pours a glass and brings the glass and pitcher to the table where Mr. Diaz has taken a seat. He drinks, Tara leans on the counter, looking back to Tiny from time to time. She notices the suitcases on one of her looks back. Mr. Diaz sees that they have her attention. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="122" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="256" ElementID="8" SceneID="255" Start="122" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The suitcases? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara turns back to Mr. Diaz. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="260" ElementID="2" SceneID="255" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I guess. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Well your husband is a very smart business man. He paid us to hold these in case what’s happened happens. You understand? A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">kinda</Text>
      <Text> insurance policy. And </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(takes a sip of juice)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">here</Text>
      <Text> I am. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is still not sure what to make of it all. She looks back to the suitcases. Mr. Diaz gets up from the table. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m going to go. I’ll give you a call in a couple of days to let you know what’s next. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s expected of you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz puts back on his hat and moves to the door. Tiny beats him there and opens it for him. Before leaving the apartment and without turning. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good Morning Mrs. Reed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tiny doesn’t say a word. They leave. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="22" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="7/8" Page="14" Title="TARA CALLS XIOMARE IN.">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara calls in her best friend. It's apart of the plan. Though she doesn't know that Xiomare would turn on them too.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>KITCHEN AREA - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="277" ElementID="92" SceneID="277" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is looking very serious, deep in contemplation. She seems to have been in this position for awhile. The object of her concentration are the two suitcases open, full of bags of white powder. Tara picks up the cordless phone and makes a call. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="173" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="278" ElementID="94" SceneID="277" Start="173" Length="20"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="213" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="278" ElementID="95" SceneID="277" Start="213" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="279" ElementID="2" SceneID="277" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cio</Text>
      <Text>, what’s up girl? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>On my way to drop off </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text>. I got </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>15 heads today, and one is in the chair right now. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Damn girl, you killing yourself. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> tired ass d-a-d-d-y ain’t doing </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> and it got to get done girl. What’s up with you? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Why don’t you and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> come by after you pick him up. Make it a play-date. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Play-date? What’s going on girl? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’ll talk about it when you get here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ah, OK... I’ll </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">holla</Text>
      <Text> when I’m close. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hangs up the phone, her attention back to the suitcases. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="23" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="7/8" Page="15" Title="XIOMARE TRIES TO GUESS THE BIG SECRET">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara and Ximoare walk. Xiomare tries to guess whats going on with Tara.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="297" ElementID="96" SceneID="297" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="297" ElementID="7" SceneID="297" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is at the curb letting Marco Jr out of the car after parking. Tara turns and sees Xiomare walking up the block with </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">KWENDE</Text>
      <Text> 7, her son who’s a couple of years older then young Marco. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara waits, little Marco runs to his friend. They fight, of course. Tara jogs up to join the battle. Xiomare and Tara greet after they have the boys settled and walking up the street They hug. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="300" ElementID="13" SceneID="297" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s good T? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="302" ElementID="2" SceneID="297" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m good </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cio</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>They walk behind the kids and chat. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So what’s up, what you got going, can’t be a boyfriend already. Is it?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>With a twisted lip. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No woman damn. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(looking around, over both</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>shoulders) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We should talk about it when we get inside. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare is noticing Tara’s jitters. She answers with both her eyebrows raised. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Really? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>They walk on. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="24" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="2/8" Page="16" Title="THE KIDS PLAY">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Marco Jr and Kwende play while the women talk business in the other room.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">FRONT ROOM - DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="317" ElementID="99" SceneID="317" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco Jr and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> are playing in front of the TV in the living room. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> gets up and sneaks to the bedroom door. He peeks in. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="318" ElementID="97" SceneID="317" Start="0" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="13" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="318" ElementID="96" SceneID="317" Start="13" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="48" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="318" ElementID="98" SceneID="317" Start="48" Length="2"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="25" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="3" Page="16" Title="XIOMARE AND TARA COME UP WITH THE PLAN">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara and Xiomare see that its drugs in the suitcases. They come up with the plan to bring Shawntey into it. Tara plays it like she needs some convincing. Xiomare should push. Tara she be non-committal/committal.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>BEDROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="319" ElementID="94" SceneID="319" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> is looking through the cracked door. He sees his mom and Tara standing in front of two big suitcases sitting on the bed. Both women’s eyes are big like saucers. Tara looks up to see </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> and moves to the door. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="320" ElementID="96" SceneID="319" Start="0" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="90" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="320" ElementID="92" SceneID="319" Start="90" Length="17"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="321" ElementID="2" SceneID="319" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OH </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text>, can you go play with </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara moves to the door, stepping on the other side to lead </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> back to the living room. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (O.S.) (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco got some new Hot Wheels. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco show </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text> your new cars. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare is in the bedroom looking in the two suitcases. She has a great smile on her face. She reaches in and picks up one of the kilos and feels the weight of it. She pokes a hole in it to taste the contents. The potency is written in the contortion of her face. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara steps back into the room. Xiomare is </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">gitty</Text>
      <Text>. Now they both are back in front of the suitcases. Tara’s look is back to that of contemplation. She bits her lip as she thinks. Tara speaks first. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="332" ElementID="13" SceneID="319" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>T, this is major. Whose, where, how </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">much</Text>
      <Text>....? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare can’t finish a sentence. Every time a new question comes to mind it crowds out the previous one. Xiomare takes a beat and calms herself. She reassembles her questions and tries again. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Got to be a story, let’s hear it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Seriously </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cio</Text>
      <Text>, it just fell in my lap. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Sooo</Text>
      <Text>.... Who does this belong to? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Us, I think, I guess. One of </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco’s business partners dropped it off. He didn’t tell me anything except it was for me. It’s got to be a couple of million dollars worth of stuff here, you think? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shit</Text>
      <Text>, at least. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare is bitting her lip looking at the drugs. The weight of the situation is fully on her now. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cio</Text>
      <Text> what do we do with all this? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Sell it T, of course. Or you get someone to sell it. This is some real money here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sits on the bed next to the suitcases thinking. We see a realization come across her face. Is this what Marco had in mind for her. Is this the vehicle that they should use to make right the perceived wrong they have weathered? Can she do this. Tara is no shrinking violent. She stands, her back straighter, her continence more assured. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What if we sold it? Or got other people to sell it for us. Marco was a businessman. He went to an office and moved money around. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(with a twisted lip) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Come on man you tripping. The </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">nigga</Text>
      <Text> got class but know he was moving kilos, for real. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara gets up from the bed and paces, as much trying to convince herself as Xiomare. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s true, what he was importing was drugs but... how he went about it is what I’m talking about. He was invisible for years. Being women we’re definitely invisible for the short time I’m talking about. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What about Marco Jr? Something goes wrong... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>These words hit Tara. The thought crossing her mind. Again we see Tara waver. And once again her resolve stiffens. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I can’t let the perfect be the enemy of the good. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare’s face contorts trying to understand. Finally she gives up. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> does that mean? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Xiomare both chuckle. But Xiomare moves it back to the serious. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Why T? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Because I’m going to. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sits next to Xiomare on the bed. Xiomare knows that fast life and she hesitates knowing what that world could be. She looks to Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>T, I’m with you whatever. I trust and love you, so whatever you want to do I’m with you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON XIOMARE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>But know this (a beat) this is real levels we’re talking about. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara smiles at her friend’s trust. The smile falls away when she turns back to the suitcases. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Right. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>They both seem to have gotten that hurdle out of the way when another occurs to Xiomare. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So now what do we do? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>They think for a beat more and Tara leaves the room. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="26" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1 2/8" Page="19" Title="Tara reaches out to Shawntey">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara brings Shawntey into the mix. The plan is off and running!</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>KITCHEN - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara moves into the kitchen where she grabs the cordless phone. She has to think for a minute to get the number from her memory. Xiomare comes out of the room and sits on the floor playing with the two boys and the new cars. Tara dials the number. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="48" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="388" ElementID="95" SceneID="387" Start="48" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is calling Shawntey, Marco Sr’s under</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">-</Text>
      <Text>boss in his former life. Shawntey is trying to make a go of it as a legitimate businessman. He owns a Ford dealership among other things. Clearly his talents definitely lye elsewhere. He answers the phone with all that frustration in his voice. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea, who this? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="392" ElementID="2" SceneID="387" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hello, Shawntey this is Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Well hello miss lady, wait is everything good? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No, no, we’re all safe. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good, good, hold on a minute. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(talking to someone around him) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>For Christ sake just go sale some damn cars please. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(talking to Tara again) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m sorry Tara. What’s going on, how’s are man? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>As good as he can be you know. I called to see if I could get a minute of your time. I have an... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(she thinks) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">...</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">opportunity</Text>
      <Text> that you may know a bit more about then me. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Anything for you baby girl. You name the place and time. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How about Buddha Lounge at 7... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(she looks over to Xiomare who’s signaling 8) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Or 8 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>8, I’m there. Later. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey hangs up the phone. Tara hangs up and turns to Xiomare. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>8 it is. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare shakes her head good. Tara joins the pile of fun on the floor with Xiomare, Marco Jr and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Kwende</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="84" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="419" ElementID="97" SceneID="387" Start="84" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="97" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="419" ElementID="96" SceneID="387" Start="97" Length="6"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="27" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="3/8" Page="20" Title="Shawntey's frustration">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey's motivation to make this thing work. tara has thrown him a life line.</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>I/E. SHAWNTEY ROSS FORD DEALERSHIP</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> SHOWROOM</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="420" ElementID="100" SceneID="420" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The place is deserted except for the employees. They mill about talking amongst themselves. Shawntey looks around at the empty showroom and sales lot. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="422" ElementID="1" SceneID="420" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shit</Text>
      <Text>! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey steps out of frame. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="28" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Color="#FFFF00000000" Length="1 1/8" Page="20" Title="Tara Tells Shawntey ">
        <Summary>
          <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
            <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Tara tells Shawntey that Mr. Diaz has shown himself to her. Shawntey</Text>
          </Paragraph>
        </Summary>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. BUDDHA LOUNGE - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="426" ElementID="101" SceneID="426" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>This is a cool downtown hang-out. Tonight is Acid Jazz night. A small trio rocks. The smooth sounds have the crowd in a mellow mood. Shawntey steps in the door. He scans the faces for Tara. He doesn’t see her but he sees Xiomare. A blind man could see Xiomare. She has a way of filling her clothes and drawing everyone’s attention. Xiomare is coming back to the table that she and Tara are sitting at. Shawntey sees Tara and moves to the table. Tara stands to greet him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="428" ElementID="2" SceneID="426" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(hugging and kissing</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>Shawntey on the cheek) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey you, what’s good with you? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="432" ElementID="1" SceneID="426" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m good baby girl. How you holding up? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We making it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey turns to Xiomare with his player’s smile and charm. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And who is this? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara begins to introduce Xiomare, but always the flirt Xiomare beats her to it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="440" ElementID="13" SceneID="426" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I would be Xiomare. Very nice to meet you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare and Shawntey shake hands. Xiomare is smiling big at Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No, nice to meet you </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sees that Xiomare has “it” on high and jumps in before it goes to far. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cio</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What? I’m just saying hello. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey has a seat at the table. He looks a little pensive, unsure of what Tara has in mind. Tara sits across him sizing him up. Shawntey’s eyes go down as though he has something to hide. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="29" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="21" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. SHAWNTEY ROSS’S FORD DEALERSHIP </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">OFFICE </Text>
      <Text>- day </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="451" ElementID="4" SceneID="451" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>Flashback </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey sits in behind his desk. His eyes are down and he and his body language is that of someone under pressure. He looks up. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="454" ElementID="1" SceneID="451" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t have </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> to say. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>On the other side of the desk are TWO FBI AGENTS. One sits looking very confident, the other is standing near the door looking very menacing. Agent One looks over his shoulder to the other Agent who steps forward with a digital recorder. He sits it on the desk and pushes the play button. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (TAPED) </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="457" ElementID="5" SceneID="451" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where’s this heat coming from? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (TAPED) </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="459" ElementID="8" SceneID="451" Start="0" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(thick accent) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where you think? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (TAPED) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s my guy. No way he’s bringing this down on us. We already talked about this. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (TAPED) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(thick accent) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You the one that said he was too</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>ambitious. Look into it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The Agent that put the digital recorder on the desk pushes the stop button and looks up to Shawntey who has a smile on his face. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="23" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="467" ElementID="63" SceneID="451" Start="23" Length="16"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>AGENT #1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="468" ElementID="14" SceneID="451" Start="0" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let me tell you how this is going to work. We pick up your boy and not you. How you think that’s going to look? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey looks very worried now. His eyes find his lap again. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="30" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5 1/8" Page="22" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. BUDDHA LOUNGE - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="471" ElementID="101" SceneID="471" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="471" ElementID="102" SceneID="471" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>AGENT #1 (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So what are going to do Mr. Ross </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON TARA </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON SHAWNTEY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>They both share an extended look. The waitress comes over to take orders breaking their stare. Shawntey turns his eyes back to Xiomare, who has wondered over near the stage now with her powers aimed at the band leader. He and she chat close, Xiomare can’t be defended against. If she wants or needs something from you, you’re in trouble. Tara is all business. The waitress stands at the table. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="477" ElementID="1" SceneID="471" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let me get a double shot of Patron Gold with a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Hiny</Text>
      <Text> back. And watch me sweetie, I need you to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">keep’em</Text>
      <Text> coming. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The waitress looks to Tara, she points to her glass of wine, to say she’ll have another. The waitress goes back to the bar. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="480" ElementID="2" SceneID="471" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How are your dealerships doing? I heard you got a couple of apartment buildings in Long Beach too? How’s it all treating you? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey’s</Text>
      <Text> attention comes back to Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> is more trouble then it’s worth T. You can’t imagine the complaints I’m getting from them </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucks</Text>
      <Text>. Grass to high, grass to low. I get a least two or three slip and falls for insurance dough a year. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>They’re a mess. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey sits back in the seat, rubbing his eyes with his head back. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Can’t sale a damn car to save my life, I think my best salesman has three sales for the year. The whole country is driving an Accord. I’m getting killed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(comes back to Tara) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s up with little Marco? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I think its harder on me then him. I haven’t seen it affect him yet. He’s a pretty strong kid. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey and Tara sit for a beat in uncomfortable silence again. Xiomare returns to the table and sits. She still is scanning the room. Her radar for a mark never goes off. She comes back to the conversation at the table. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tara, you know I think of Marco as </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">my</Text>
      <Text> brother and... I feel like </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> because of how things turned out I.... I have been carrying this thing since he got arrested. I don’t know who... you know. I DO know Marco is doubting me right now. So I’m glad you call. I want to make it right in his eyes, you know. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No worries, its a part of the business that Marco was in. We’ll survive. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(smiling) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Maybe something will come of it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">XIOMARE</Text>
      <Text> JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="501" ElementID="13" SceneID="471" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> talking ‘bout? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> and Tara smile at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare’s</Text>
      <Text> timing. But Tara takes the opportunity to move it along. The waitress comes back and lays out the drinks in front of everybody, then moves away. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> downs the double shot in no time. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text>, what could you tell me about Mr. Diaz? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey’s</Text>
      <Text> beer comes flying out of his nose and mouth. Tara and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare</Text>
      <Text> look at each other. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> regains his composure. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where did that come from? Why you asking? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re asking. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK, ah, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Xiomare are hanging on Shawntey’s words. Almost on the edge of their seats, they’re leaning into the conversation. Shawntey sees that they must know something and decides not to soften it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Aight</Text>
      <Text>, Marco is a Columbian with connects to the cartels. With Marco’s international connection importing and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> he and the Diaz guy started moving stuff up here. Slowly Marco and I saw the value of us making a few moves for ourselves. Once it got rolling, you know the rest. Marco was the only person that really dealt with him. I’ve tried a bunch of times to get him to let me ride with him, or even to let me get the connect myself. He claim the guy wouldn’t deal with me. I was beginning to think he didn’t even exist. I never meet him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey looks at the ladies, they seem to think that there’s more to the story. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s it? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea that’s it. What’s going on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">ya’ll</Text>
      <Text>? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(sitting up in his seat) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Why </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> call me here? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies sit back in their seats, half smiles on their faces. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara leans forward, taking the lead. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>He came to see me. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Not believing his ears. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Who? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz came to the house. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> sits back in his seat. A range of emotion pass his face. Amazed that the mythical Mr. Diaz has shown himself, but up-set that he didn’t come to him. Happy to be back in the middle of the game, mad that he wasn’t the one chosen. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="91" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="536" ElementID="8" SceneID="471" Start="91" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>He made me an offer, I think. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> this is your world, these are your people, I need your help. He said that he would come back in a couple of days to show me what would be expected. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Expected! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">XIOMARE</Text>
      <Text> JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea baby its going down. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> I’m going to make this happen, run it like Marco, like a business. Where we are in the chain of things we won’t have to do much street work right? We just need to fire up the import connects Marco used and know how to move the money. I can work the money. I know the cracks in the financial system. I love Marco, but he got tripped up by his ego. There’s a time to step away and evolve into another stage in life. This won’t be a lifestyle for us. I need your help to pull it though. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey sits for a beat, then finds the waitress’ eyes and waves for another round of drinks. He rubs his face with his hands, thinking. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tara you know what your asking for? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Don’t you think its a bit much now, with Marco gone away? What about the boy? What about you? I know you want to run it like a business and all that but this is not a business for the faint at heart. They can and will test you, especially some women. What happens when they come at you, come at us, because they most definitely will? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>They! Who the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> is they? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey snaps at Xiomare. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The jungle and every animal in it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara drops her head, this is a touchy subject for her. Tara lifts her head and looks intently at Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="557" ElementID="293" SceneID="471" Start="0" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m committed Shawntey. I know from </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco that in a fight, it comes down to who’s the most committed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey shakes his head no and sits back in his seat. He’s not buying any of it. Xiomare mouths “damn”, impress with Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I have a 18 month window, then I’m out. Once I have my family back, YOU can have the connect, and build your own thing or, retire like us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey’s face contorts not liking that last idea. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The ladies I called to be apart of this are meeting at my house tomorrow. Think about it and come through. We do need your insight in this market place. You’ll see that we’re serious about this. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey thinks it over for a beat. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I can’t promise nothing. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare smiles big. Tara leans back in her chair. Shawntey is looking confused and unsure what to make of this. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="31" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="27" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT</Text>
      <Text> HALLWAY- NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="571" ElementID="1" SceneID="571" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="571" ElementID="13" SceneID="571" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A man climbs up the last stair to Tara’s apartment. He knocks at Tara’s door. We still haven’t seen his face. The sound of the chain being put on the door can be heard. The door opens. Xiomare cracks the door. She studies the face of this unseen man. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      </UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="32" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="6/8" Page="27" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">FRONT ROOM </Text>
      <Text>- </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="5" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="573" ElementID="9" SceneID="573" Start="5" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="573" ElementID="16" SceneID="573" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>It’s Shawntey at the door. He steps in. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="575" ElementID="13" SceneID="573" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey you. Tara is right over there </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">let</Text>
      <Text> me get her. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="578" ElementID="1" SceneID="573" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cool. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(looking into the room) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OH </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare closes the door behind him and moves to Tara. Shawntey stands in the doorway just looking. He’s definitely liking what he sees. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The front room is filled with beautiful ladies. Xiomare taps Tara and she turns to see Shawntey. She steps away from her conversation and comes over to him. They hug. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where’s my man. I got him a car. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey pulls a Hot Wheel from his jacket pocket. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="15" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="586" ElementID="103" SceneID="573" Start="15" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="587" ElementID="2" SceneID="573" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>He’s at his grandmother’s until I can make this place safe. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Look T, I’m not promising... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(raises his eyebrows) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Safe? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="33" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="6/8" Page="28" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>BEDROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="593" ElementID="92" SceneID="593" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="593" ElementID="94" SceneID="593" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The open suitcases sit on the bed. Shawntey’s eyes are big looking over the possibilities. Tara leans on the wall behind him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="595" ElementID="2" SceneID="593" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Safe! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="597" ElementID="1" SceneID="593" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> T. This is ah, interesting. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey picks up the kilo that Xiomare took a taste from. He does the same. His face contorts the same as hers. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea this is him. Wow T, this is </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">big</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey stands up and starts pacing, thinking. His wheels are turning big time. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What did he say, what’s the rate? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How many can we get? Is it consignment or what? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Slow down big boy, I see you back huh. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(smiling) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Grab the stuff and let’s move to the front room. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara walks into the front room. A beat later, his composure renewed, Shawntey closes the cases, grabs them up and moves to the front room as well. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="34" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="29" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>FRONT ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="612" ElementID="9" SceneID="612" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="612" ElementID="16" SceneID="612" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="612" ElementID="13" SceneID="612" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="612" ElementID="1" SceneID="612" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="612" ElementID="92" SceneID="612" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara back into the front room followed by Shawntey momentarily. He’s carrying the two suitcases. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="614" ElementID="2" SceneID="612" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Before we start, we all know each other. Let me introduce you all to </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Shawntey. He worked with Marco </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(turns to Shawntey) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">and</Text>
      <Text> he’s a good guy. He’s going to introduce us and our product to the world. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies are gather around the small coffee table in front of the couch. Xiomare is sitting on the floor next to the coffee table. She’s dressed as sexy as the law would allow. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON XIOMARE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE:  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="35" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="29" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. SHOPPING MALL UNDERGROUND PARKING - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">FLASH FORWARD</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare pulls next to a black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> similar to the one she’s driving. Two men sit in the truck smoking cigarettes. The man in the driver's seat is BIG FOLKS 37. He gets out of the truck, reaches in the back seat and gets a briefcase. He walks over to Xiomare's </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="624" ElementID="13" SceneID="622" Start="0" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="22" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="624" ElementID="104" SceneID="622" Start="22" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="145" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="624" ElementID="105" SceneID="622" Start="145" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="219" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="624" ElementID="106" SceneID="622" Start="219" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>She steps out of the truck and they both move to the hood. He hands her the briefcase, she takes it and cracks it looking in. She runs her fingers through a few stacks of hundreds to make sure that it’s all money. Xiomare closes the case with a smile and flips the keys over her shoulder to Big Folks who is checking her out the whole time. Xiomare walks towards the mall, she turns and gives Big Folks a wink and a smile, still the flirt. She continues in the mall. Big Folks now has the back hatch up looking into the portion of the truck where the spare is and it is filled with what looks like bricks wrapped in brown paper.  </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="265" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="625" ElementID="42" SceneID="622" Start="265" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="598" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="625" ElementID="107" SceneID="622" Start="598" Length="29"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Xiomare you already met. She’ll be our logistics person. She’ll pick up money, deliver the product to * buyers, whatever we need. As you * can see she’s a weapon. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="36" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="30" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT - LIVING ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="628" ElementID="16" SceneID="628" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="628" ElementID="2" SceneID="628" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="628" ElementID="1" SceneID="628" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare greets Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="630" ElementID="13" SceneID="628" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s happening big boy?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON KIM PEREZ 30, a sexy and curvaceous lady. Soft in her style and persona. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="632" ElementID="9" SceneID="628" Start="9" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE:  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="37" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="30" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. BANK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">LOBBY </Text>
      <Text>- DAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">FLASH FORWARD</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim shakes hands with MR. WILLIAMSON 52 in the lobby of the * bank. They move to Mr. Williamson’s desk.  Kim and Mr. Williamson sit at his desk chatting. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="22" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="636" ElementID="34" SceneID="634" Start="22" Length="14"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="636" ElementID="9" SceneID="634" Start="0" Length="3"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This is Kim, she’ll be working on the banking side. Doing the wash. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="38" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="30" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS OFFICE - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">FLASH FORWARD</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim sits behind the big desk, she has the same kind of work area as she did in her office at the bank. She has charts, trend line sheets and graphs. Her computer screen has the same look from her office.  </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="641" ElementID="9" SceneID="639" Start="0" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="111" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="641" ElementID="108" SceneID="639" Start="111" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="119" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="641" ElementID="109" SceneID="639" Start="119" Length="17"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="141" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="641" ElementID="110" SceneID="639" Start="141" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="153" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="641" ElementID="76" SceneID="639" Start="153" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Kim has work at several security companies like Merrill Lynch and Chase Securities Management among others, basically doing their wash too. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(chuckles) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="39" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="31" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT LIVING ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="645" ElementID="13" SceneID="645" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim acknowledges Shawntey.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>KIM PEREZ </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="647" ElementID="9" SceneID="645" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Aye pappi </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey is looking at this beauty and speaks under his breathe. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="650" ElementID="1" SceneID="645" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(under his breath) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wow! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hears him and turns to him with a smile. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="654" ElementID="2" SceneID="645" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I know right! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Next is Cassidy Redman, Tara’s muscle. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="8" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="656" ElementID="16" SceneID="645" Start="8" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON CASSIDY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="40" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="31" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">GTS</Text>
      <Text> UNLIMITED FIREARMS RANGE - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="658" ElementID="16" SceneID="658" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="658" ElementID="9" SceneID="658" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="658" ElementID="2" SceneID="658" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="658" ElementID="1" SceneID="658" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="658" ElementID="13" SceneID="658" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="658" ElementID="87" SceneID="658" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="658" ElementID="44" SceneID="658" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">FLASH FORWARD</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>All of the ladies are standing around one of the stalls in the empty gun range. Cassidy is putting on a display. The shots she shoots pepper the center of the target. The ladies are very impressed. Shawntey has to give it up to her too. They all clap. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="134" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="660" ElementID="111" SceneID="658" Start="134" Length="31"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This is Cassidy, Iraq war vet, Army </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Range and our security. She don’t play. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="41" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 6/8" Page="31" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT LIVING ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="664" ElementID="1" SceneID="664" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="664" ElementID="92" SceneID="664" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="664" ElementID="94" SceneID="664" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy gives Shawntey a head nod, like one of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fellas</Text>
      <Text>. Tara turns back to Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="666" ElementID="2" SceneID="664" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ladies this is Shawntey. He worked with Marco for a number of years. He has the inside knowledge and experience in this world. He knows the players and the pretenders. He’s going to be our tour guide for our little run. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(looking at Shawntey) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And that’s our crew. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(turning back to the ladies) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So I need to talk to each of you to go over how this will play. The few things that are most important are; we don’t mess with our product. You do, you’re out. We always are, looking, acting, and representing as ladies. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(turns to Shawntey) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Except for you Shawntey, of course. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And finally, follow the security guidelines that you’ll receive. No one will get hurt, no one will go to jail. All right, now let’s talk.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>KIM PEREZ </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="675" ElementID="9" SceneID="664" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Don’t use the product. Are we talking about drugs? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="678" ElementID="16" SceneID="664" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(not to pleased) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Drugs? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara turns to Cassidy to answer her question. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="682" ElementID="13" SceneID="664" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea T, what’s in the suitcases. Let them see what were talking about. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara gives Xiomare the stink eye. She nods to Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>In here, on the kitchen table. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey grabs up the cases and moves to the kitchen, followed by the ladies. Shawntey swings the heavy cases on the table and opens them up. The “damns” are loud, fired one after another. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It is drugs. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>KIM PEREZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tara I can’t be apart of this. I’m not... I don’t want anything to.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim moves back to the couch where her sweater is. She picks it up. She’s met there by Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Kim, come on now. Don’t think about it like that, think of it as a product, a cash rich product. We’re imports. Besides ma, you have a MBA, smart as hell and still you got to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> somebody to make some real money. I asked you when I saw you if you wanted a way out. Here it is. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(pointing towards the suitcases) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>After this you won’t have to work, much less for some creepy </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucks</Text>
      <Text>, ever again. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara turns to the rest of the ladies, Cassidy too is looking not to sure of this course. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I had problems like the rest of you about what I’m proposing. I tried to drag Marco out this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> a thousand times, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> know what the hell I been through. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="42" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="33" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED FAMILY MANSION </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> JUST INSIDE DOOR</Text>
      <Text>- NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Looking at the front door of this beautiful home, Marco Sr comes in at full speed, he moves through the house looking for Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="703" ElementID="5" SceneID="700" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>T... Tara... Tara... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="43" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="33" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">REED FAMILY MANSION </Text>
      <Text>UPSTAIRS - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="705" ElementID="97" SceneID="705" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="705" ElementID="60" SceneID="705" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="705" ElementID="2" SceneID="705" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco Sr moves up the stairs, down the hallway opening and closing doors. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.)  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t ever want that feeling again...  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>He comes to the bathroom, opens the door finding a surprised Tara giving baby Marco a bath. Her face changes from the happy mommy to the same fear she sees in Marco’s eyes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And I’m determine...  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>SPLIT SCREEN BEGINS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>As Marco mouths words, the screen splits. Marco on the left  side and on the right side... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="44" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="34" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">REED FAMILY MANSION </Text>
      <Text>LIVING ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="714" ElementID="112" SceneID="714" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="714" ElementID="113" SceneID="714" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="714" ElementID="114" SceneID="714" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco races down the stairs. He moves to the front room and the fireplace. He reaches into the flute and pulls down a silver fire retardant bag. He unzips it to check the contents, it’s full of cash. The police finally have the door smashed in. Marco makes a futile attempt to make a dash for the back door. The officers come in the back door trapping  him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>POLICE OFFICER #4 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="716" ElementID="17" SceneID="714" Start="0" Length="17"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(mouths) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Show me your hands! Get on the floor. Show me your hands! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The officers tackle him a few steps away. Tara stands at the top of the stairs holding Marco Jr. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="87" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="719" ElementID="7" SceneID="714" Start="87" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="720" ElementID="2" SceneID="714" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(mouths) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>NO! He’s not resisting! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.) (CONT’D)  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text> I didn’t choose this...  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>END OF FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="45" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2 1/8" Page="34" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT FRONT ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="726" ElementID="92" SceneID="726" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="726" ElementID="94" SceneID="726" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="727" ElementID="2" SceneID="726" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This opportunity fell on me and</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> with the markets crashing  every other day... I want to take it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(after a beat) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Men take the bull by the horns all the time. It’s our turn. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(pacing) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I can be scared and like the rest of you think of what could happen, all of those bad things. OR, I could approach this like the business that I learned to manage at university. I can take this opportunity. I’m in it to get out of here. When Marco gets out we’re leaving the country, a fresh start. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Just give me 18 months and the rest of your life will be whatever you want it to be. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara looks all the ladies in their eyes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Xiomare what do you want to do? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="737" ElementID="13" SceneID="726" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m with you sister, you know that. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cassidy? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="741" ElementID="16" SceneID="726" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">kinda</Text>
      <Text> numbers we talking about? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(turns to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text>) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="746" ElementID="1" SceneID="726" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Depends. You want to mash the gas and get the money we could do a million a week maybe more. That’s serious money. Marco never wanted to be full out like that. He had the nice mix of legit business and this. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(turns to Tara) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m in. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Everyone reacts to the big number. Tara just smiles. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wow. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea that’s what I’m talking about. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sets her eyes on Kim who raises her eyebrows when she hears the big number. Kim is sitting on the couch looking at her hands obviously conflicted with this choice. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>KIM PEREZ </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="756" ElementID="9" SceneID="726" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(not looking up) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t want that stuff nowhere near me. I only deal with money. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Sweet. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>On that note Tara pulls Shawntey to the side to chat privately. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(to the ladies) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Excuse us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(now to Shawntey privately) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I need some start up money, Shawn. We need money for setting up accounts, for uniforms, weapons, counter surveillance, to get that stuff out of my house so I can bring my baby back home. We need money. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I know what you need, when did Diaz say he was coming back? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(thinking) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wait uniforms? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>He said a couple of days yesterday, but what the hell do I know. I wasn’t expecting him in the first place. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll come back tomorrow with a couple of bucks.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey holds up his finger, as though to say wait a minute. He leaves the room. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="46" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="36" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>BEDROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey comes into the room and grabs a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SPONGEBOB</Text>
      <Text> backpack that’s lying on the floor. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="47" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1" Page="36" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>FRONT ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="778" ElementID="13" SceneID="778" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="778" ElementID="9" SceneID="778" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="778" ElementID="94" SceneID="778" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Back in the front room with Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="780" ElementID="1" SceneID="778" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let me use this. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey goes to the suitcases and puts one of the kilos in the backpack, zips it up and comes back to Tara. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="64" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="782" ElementID="115" SceneID="778" Start="64" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="21" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="782" ElementID="92" SceneID="778" Start="21" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Get’em</Text>
      <Text> ready ma, its about to get real, quick. I’ll </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">holla</Text>
      <Text> at you tomorrow. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey steps from Tara, over to the ladies as they chat about what they’ve just signed up for. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good night ladies, Let’s make this happen. Don’t worry, I wouldn’t let anything happen to any of you. I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">got’cha</Text>
      <Text> you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies all say goodbye relatively at the same time. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>ALL THE LADIES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="789" ElementID="294" SceneID="778" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Bye. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey walks out of the door, Tara brings it back to business. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="792" ElementID="2" SceneID="778" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Come on ladies. If you’re in, you’re in. Let’s straighten up those faces and make this business happen. Cassidy can you put the suitcases back in the bedroom. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="794" ElementID="16" SceneID="778" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Got’cha</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy goes to the table and closes the suitcases and moves them into the bedroom. Tara’s voice fades out as does the picture. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Now, the first thing is security. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cassidy will instruct us all in the </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">use</Text>
      <Text> of fire arms (fading) Kim’s head pops up not expecting to hear that. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="48" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="38" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT BEDROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is startled awake. There’s a constant banging on her apartment door. She looks at the clock on the table next to the bed. It reads: 7:02 am. Tara scrambles to her feet, half out of fear, half still sleep. She’s dressed in only the shorts and T-shirt that she was sleeping in. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="803" ElementID="2" SceneID="802" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="91" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="803" ElementID="116" SceneID="802" Start="91" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="236" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="803" ElementID="117" SceneID="802" Start="236" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="247" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="803" ElementID="118" SceneID="802" Start="247" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="49" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="38" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">TARA REED’S APARTMENT </Text>
      <Text>FRONT ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The knocking, almost unbroken, keeps it’s rapid pace. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Coming, coming. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara reaches the door puts the chain on the door and cracks it. A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Spongebob</Text>
      <Text> Square Pants backpack is thrust through the crack. It’s half closed but clearly Tara can see money bursting out of the top of it. Tara takes the backpack, unzips it and takes in the full view of the bag of money. Tara forgets about the person at the door. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="66" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="808" ElementID="119" SceneID="804" Start="66" Length="31"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="169" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="808" ElementID="120" SceneID="804" Start="169" Length="18"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Don’t forget about your boy out here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="811" ElementID="2" SceneID="804" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Oh </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>, sorry Shawn. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara turns back to the door takes the chain off and opens it. Shawntey steps in. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="814" ElementID="1" SceneID="804" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good morning. Can I buy you a cup of coffee, unless you made some. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Boy I was dead sleep three minutes ago. Let me put something on real quick. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara goes back towards her bed room tossing the bag on the kitchen table. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SPONGEBOB</Text>
      <Text> SQUARE PANTS BACKPACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 6/8" Page="38" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. COFFEE JOINT - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A LA Times hits the table. Tara sits down at the table in this morning coffee joint. Hot donuts and fresh newspapers are their specialty. Shawntey is already sitting, drinking a large orange juice. He looks as though he just won the big game, the excitement is written on his face. Tara has a bottled water next to her as she reads the business section. After a quick glance, she closes it, setting it aside to concentrate on Shawntey. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="63" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="822" ElementID="121" SceneID="821" Start="63" Length="14"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="176" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="822" ElementID="122" SceneID="821" Start="176" Length="20"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="291" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="822" ElementID="123" SceneID="821" Start="291" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="823" ElementID="2" SceneID="821" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How much is that? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="825" ElementID="1" SceneID="821" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>135K, and T that’s just the beginning. The places I took that to all were crazy excited that Marco’s quality was back. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>(</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">leaning</Text>
      <Text> into Tara) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I got everybody here but Vincent to come see you, and I got calls in with four or five heavy players from the Midwest, the East Coast and the Bay. This is going to be big ma. Those numbers I said yesterday, I was just talking out of my ass. This could be that big if not bigger. (A beat) What’s up with Mr. Diaz? We need to know how this works. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I guess today, tomorrow. I’m not sure how this works either or what we owe already. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(bitting her lip) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sits back in the booth, thinking. A small smile spreads across her face, she almost forgets that Shawntey is there. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So what’s next? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey’s questions startles Tara, lost in her own daydreams. After a beat she regains her place in the conversation. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ahh</Text>
      <Text>... We set up the fronts and get ready for the wash. The rest depends on the deal I can get with Mr. Diaz. He’s going to have the import connects to... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Huh? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The deal WE can get with Mr. Diaz. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m your partner over here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea, we of course. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara rolls right over the slight that Shawntey is keen to notice. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>All that in place, we meet your people, then we’re open for business..... (a beat) Oh </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>, what time you got? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara pats her pockets looking for her cell. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="38" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="851" ElementID="124" SceneID="821" Start="38" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I forgot my cell. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ah, 8:10. Why what’s up? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I got to get home my mother is bringing Marco back a 8:30 before she goes to work. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara stands up and collects her paper. Shawntey follows, downing the last of his </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">OJ</Text>
      <Text>. He tosses the cup in the trash. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="32" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="858" ElementID="125" SceneID="821" Start="32" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="51" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="40" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S APARTMENT FRONT ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara steps through the door of her apartment. She takes off her jacket, tossing it on the couch and walks towards the bathroom. When she steps from view there’s a knock at the door. This one is a lot more polite. Tara knows who this is. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="861" ElementID="2" SceneID="859" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(yelling from the next room) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Coming ma! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara appears from the bathroom toweling her hands dry. She goes to the door and quickly opens it. Its not her mother but Tiny filling the doorway. Tara is taken back. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="31" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="864" ElementID="126" SceneID="859" Start="31" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shit</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tiny gives Tara a head nod to go. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK let me get my jacket. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara turns to get her jacket, Tiny grabs her on the shoulder, not hard enough to hurt just enough to get her full attention. Tiny leads Tara out the door. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="30" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="870" ElementID="78" SceneID="859" Start="30" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK, no jacket. I hope we’re not </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">walking</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="52" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="41" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. TARA REED’</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">S </Text>
      <Text>APARTMENT - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> is parked at the curb in front of Tara’s building. Tiny follows Tara to the truck, opens the back door for her and she gets in. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="875" ElementID="104" SceneID="874" Start="0" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="63" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="875" ElementID="78" SceneID="874" Start="63" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="76" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="875" ElementID="2" SceneID="874" Start="76" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="53" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3" Page="41" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. INSIDE MR. DIAZ’S </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SUV</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="876" ElementID="104" SceneID="876" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara lands in her seat. Mr. Diaz is sitting on the opposite side in an expensive suit as usual. He has a huge cigar in his fingers. Tara looks him over, the little things, his manicure, the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Rolex</Text>
      <Text> Presidential, the cuff links all smack of money. Mr. Diaz is a man of style as well as opportunity. Tiny lands in his seat in the front. He turns and waves the radio receiver thing over Tara, the same as he did the first time they met. Tiny nods to Mr. Diaz. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="24" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="877" ElementID="8" SceneID="876" Start="24" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="190" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="877" ElementID="128" SceneID="876" Start="190" Length="18"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="103" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="877" ElementID="129" SceneID="876" Start="103" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="356" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="877" ElementID="91" SceneID="876" Start="356" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="878" ElementID="2" SceneID="876" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Radio wave detector. A device that detects if you’re wearing a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">mic</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">. C</Text>
      <Text>ounter surveillance, I spend more money on it then food. You </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">gonna</Text>
      <Text> do the same if you’re going to be in this business. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Am I? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>In this business? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The driver of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>, at least as big as Tiny starts the truck and pulls away. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="889" ElementID="127" SceneID="876" Start="0" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good right to the point, very much like Marco. (a beat) What did you think of the suitcases? You did open them? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea I opened them. I’m not scared if that’s what you’re asking. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">OOOhhh</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(half laughing) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You hear that Tiny, she’s not scared. Well Mrs. Reed if you ain’t scared, you ain’t </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">doin</Text>
      <Text> it right. Scared is good, scared keeps you safe. Strategy without tactics is the slowest route to victory. Tactics without strategy is the noise before defeat. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Sun Tzu. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz’s head snaps to Tara, surprised she knows the quote. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s right. Very good. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(gives Tara a nod) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I told your husband the same thing. It served him well. He just needed to be a better judge of friends. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>This odd comment strikes Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What? What do you know about </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco’s friends? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Be committed Mrs. Re</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">e</Text>
      <Text>d because once we start this, it ain’t for play.</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> T</Text>
      <Text>he </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fellas</Text>
      <Text> are going to want your position and they may not be nice about asking for it. You understand what I’m saying to you? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yes I do. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz sizes Tara up. Tara’s cells rings. She looks at it . The caller ID reads; MOMMA. Mr. Diaz notices.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Everything OK? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ahhh</Text>
      <Text> yea, sure. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We need to turn back? We can do this tomorrow. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m here now. Let’s finish it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK, we do this once a month until you get your feet under you. $6,500 per on consignment. I’ll contact * you two days before the drop to get your order. Here... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz hands Tara a cell. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="20" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="924" ElementID="90" SceneID="876" Start="20" Length="6"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t call to talk. I’ll send you picture messages that have the place and the time. You do the same for the number of units. To keep it clear that it’s you and I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">texting</Text>
      <Text>, the order is a picture of the number of units, then a picture of you. I’ll go picture of place then the time. In that order. Always that order, if it comes in another, it ain’t me. The same for you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(pauses thinking) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let’s see what else... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara cell rings again. She slides it under her leg as she  talks. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="929" ElementID="130" SceneID="876" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The suitcases. How much do I owe you for them? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Oh no. They’re yours. You owe me nothing. Marco paid for that long ago. As I said, a very smart man. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What about getting it here? Do I have anything to do with that? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No that’s covered in your per unit cost. Besides the people I work for wouldn’t be excited to have you involved with any of that. OK, you and one other come to the drops. I’ll never make this hard for you, always clean vehicles, great packs, safe enough for you to drive in the city. What else, oh never.... (</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fades</Text>
      <Text>) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>As Mr. Diaz’s voice fades the CAMERA pulls back through the rear of the trick, through the back window and watches the vehicle drive away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="54" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2" Page="44" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. TORRES HOUSE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="940" ElementID="71" SceneID="940" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Flowers line the sidewalk of this modest home. This house has been loved and care for. Marco Jr and Tara walk up the pathway to the steps. Tara carries Marco Jr’s small suitcase. Mother and son climb the stairs. Tara stops and bends to her knees to talk face to face with Marco Jr. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="272" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="941" ElementID="7" SceneID="940" Start="272" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="163" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="941" ElementID="131" SceneID="940" Start="163" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="942" ElementID="2" SceneID="940" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I need you to be a good boy for grandma. Momma has to go out of town for a job. I’ll be back in a couple of weeks. When I get back we’ll go to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Disneyland</Text>
      <Text> or Magic </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Mountain. You choose. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO JR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(shouting with excitement) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Disneyland</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Disneyland</Text>
      <Text> it is. But I need you to be mommy’s little man until I get back. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO JR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No worries ma. I’ll take care of grandma. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Little Marco’s strength eases Tara. She smiles at what sounds and feels like his father. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You are your daddy’s son. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara gives him a kiss and stands. She knocks and MRS. TORRES 55, a brown skin Hispanic woman answers the door. This is Tara’s mom. She’s dressed in a house coat and slippers. Her half-glasses around her neck on a string. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="148" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="955" ElementID="132" SceneID="940" Start="148" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="165" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="955" ElementID="133" SceneID="940" Start="165" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="179" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="955" ElementID="134" SceneID="940" Start="179" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO JR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(excited) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Grandma! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MRS. TORRES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="959" ElementID="19" SceneID="940" Start="0" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey baby. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco Jr hugs his grandmother the goes in the house </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey ma. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara steps in and gives her mother a kiss on the check. Ms. Torres pats Tara on the back as they embrace. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MS. TORRES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="965" ElementID="20" SceneID="940" Start="0" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How are you baby? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m good, missing Marco you know. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How are you? How’s the leg? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Ms. Torres looks over Tara’s shoulder and sees Xiomare sitting in Tara’s car waiting. Ms. Torres is no dummy, especially after the drama that Marco’s situation has caused their entire family. Ms. Torres’ eyes squint seeing through the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">bullshit</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MS. TORRES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">kinda</Text>
      <Text> job is it if she’s going? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara knows where this is going. She reaches out to little Marco who’s standing behind his grandmother. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll call you when I get there. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO JR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK momma. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Ms. Torres has her lip twisted not buying the story. Tara kisses Ms. Torres on the cheek and turns and walks off the stairs saying over her shoulder. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll call when we get to the hotel ma. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MS. TORRES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(said through twisted lip) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK baby, you be safe. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Ms. Torres watches, Marco behind her side. Xiomare gets out of the driver’s door running around to the passenger’s side, as Tara comes back to the car. Xiomare is dress crazy sexy as usual. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="985" ElementID="13" SceneID="940" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey Ms. Torres </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Ms. Torres waves back. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MS. TORRES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(under her breathe) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What the hell is she wearing? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare and Tara drive away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="55" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1" Page="46" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="992" ElementID="9" SceneID="992" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="992" ElementID="1" SceneID="992" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="992" ElementID="16" SceneID="992" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Xiomare walk down the hallway looking for a number on the door. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="994" ElementID="2" SceneID="992" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Here we go 640. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara turns the knob and goes in. Xiomare follows. The rest of the crew are inside drinking Champagne out of red party cups. They all cheer when Tara comes in. Xiomare is struck by this loft office. Hardwood floors, 15’ ceilings, exposed brink and two levels. Xiomare is looking around not noticing the people. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="91" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="996" ElementID="135" SceneID="992" Start="91" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="109" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="996" ElementID="136" SceneID="992" Start="109" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="997" ElementID="13" SceneID="992" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Damn girl! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare loosen from her trace has wondered over to the only furniture in the room, a lone desk where the champagne is being served. Xiomare gets her and Tara a cup. She walks it over to Tara. Tara takes the cup then calls the room to order. Shawntey finds his way to Tara’s right side. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>LADIES, LADIES. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The conversations settle. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This is our house, I’m calling it </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Reed Holdings. Security will be here tomorrow to do the secure telephone and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">DSL</Text>
      <Text> lines. You will be able to talk and work on-line here and only here safely, nowhere else. Everyone got that? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>They all shake their heads yes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t care, as long as we can get the money. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies chuckle, Xiomare is a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">jokester</Text>
      <Text> too. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We have a very important meeting tomorrow night. If it goes well, we’ll open with a bang. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>All the ladies cheer. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      </UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="56" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="47" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NEIMAN</Text>
      <Text> MARCUS - LADIES’ DESIGNER AREA - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1013" ElementID="9" SceneID="1013" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1013" ElementID="1" SceneID="1013" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1013" ElementID="2" SceneID="1013" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1013" ElementID="13" SceneID="1013" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1013" ElementID="16" SceneID="1013" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1013" ElementID="137" SceneID="1013" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">FLASH FORWARD</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>In a three-way mirror in the designer’s area of the store, Kim, Xiomare, Cassidy, Shawntey and Tara try on different looks. The clothes they are putting on look like big money. They look as though they are a board of a Fortune 500 company. The only person having problems finding a look that they and Tara can agree to is Xiomare. She wants more skin to show in everything and Tara wants her to look like money not sex. Tara and Xiomare find a look that they can agree on. Xiomare begrudgingly agrees. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED  (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We need to look the part of multi- million dollar investment managers. And ladies remember that’s what we are. We’re criminals like the Kennedy’s or Melons.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Who? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Anyway we’re business women. Don’t get me wrong though, we’re no paper dolls. If you don’t pay... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="57" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2 1/8" Page="48" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS OFFICE - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="86" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1022" ElementID="13" SceneID="1022" Start="86" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1022" ElementID="135" SceneID="1022" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1022" ElementID="136" SceneID="1022" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON CASSIDY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1024" ElementID="16" SceneID="1022" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Off with your head. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>This brings a little smile to Tara and raised eyebrows from the rest of the room. This is a hint of things to come. They are taking on the personas of their roles </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1027" ElementID="2" SceneID="1022" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Alright I’ll chat with each of you about what’s next. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies start to get back to their conversations. Tara turns to Shawntey and taps him to follow her. They move to Cassidy. Tara touches Cassidy on the arm to get her attention. Cassidy and Tara are standing close talking business. Shawntey closes the circle. Tara looks deep into Cassidy’s eyes </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You ready for this Cass. This is going to get real. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy has a rye smile at the comment. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I got you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara touches Cassidy on the cheek nodding OK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Can you put together a list of weapons that we’ll need. Everything you can think of to make us safe. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Safe huh? What </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">kinda</Text>
      <Text> money we talking about? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No worries on money. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara steps to the side and puts her hands on Shawntey’s shoulders. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Shawntey will help you find whatever you can’t find on your own. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1045" ElementID="1" SceneID="1022" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Can you touch a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">GSG</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">5HK</Text>
      <Text>? I been trying to get that joint for a minute? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I can </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">holla</Text>
      <Text> at my boy at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">FortBragg</Text>
      <Text>. He might be able to touch a few things for us. Not sure about a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">HK</Text>
      <Text>. I got a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">hommie</Text>
      <Text> in Russia too that can get </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> like that. It’s a new world you know. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey raises an eyebrow. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Damn! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara leaves Shawntey and Cassidy building on security and moves over to Kim. She’s in the corner by herself reading a magazine. She’s dressed rather conservatively in a dress that shows none of her curves, glasses and flat shoes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Kim we need to talk about setting up accounts. Can we do a few Cayman or St. Croix accounts, or do we spread them over Europe? I hear Liechtenstein is a nice haven. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>KIM PEREZ </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1055" ElementID="9" SceneID="1022" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Homeland security is squeezing all the old ways. But first we need to come up with a work-flow. Moving large sums of physical money out of the country is going to be a task in itself. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim ponders for a bit. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>KIM PEREZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I went to school with a guy that’s at Bank of The Americas that might be able to set us up, of course for a fee. Getting the money digital is more costly then it use to be. The juice is as high as 45%...(a beat) But once its digital we can move it anyway. I’ll figure out a place. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good let’s talk about that. Let me get another cup of Champagne. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON TARA as she walks away from Kim. Tara has it all in place. She looks into the LENS with confidence, even arrogance. A small little smile spreads across her face as she moves. The picture goes from real time to slow motion. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="58" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="50" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. LONG BEACH PIER 79 - ENTRANCE - ENTRANCE - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1064" ElementID="2" SceneID="1064" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>All but Kim is in the black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>, one of Shawntey’s from his dealership. They ride in silence a few blocks. Everyone has a bit of nerves working. They pull up to the entrance to the pier. There are a couple of POLICE OFFICERS standing on either side of a police barrier. Everyone in the truck notices. Tara looks at Shawntey. He gives her a nod of confidence. But not all in the truck saw the move and the apprehension permeates the truck. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="22" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1065" ElementID="104" SceneID="1064" Start="22" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="199" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1065" ElementID="138" SceneID="1064" Start="199" Length="25"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="254" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1065" ElementID="139" SceneID="1064" Start="254" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1066" ElementID="13" SceneID="1064" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So what‘s this mean? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey pulls up to the officer on his side of the truck. The officer looks into the car. He sees Shawntey and his face eases. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>POLICE OFFICER #1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1069" ElementID="21" SceneID="1064" Start="0" Length="17"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What up dog? They’re back there </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">waiting</Text>
      <Text> on you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey and the officer slap a pound. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1073" ElementID="1" SceneID="1064" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cool. You looking real good in that </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>monkey suit. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey says half laughing at the officer. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>POLICE OFFICER #1 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>But I still keeps it hood though. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(points to his shoes) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>He has on some crispy new white Air Force Ones, loose straps and all. Shawntey leans out the truck to check his kicks. He chuckles. He puts the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> in drive and pulls off. The truck fades into the blackness of the distance. The fake officer returns the barrier to its blocking position. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="59" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2 6/8" Page="50" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. LONG BEACH PIER 79 - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1081" ElementID="44" SceneID="1081" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1081" ElementID="43" SceneID="1081" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1081" ElementID="148" SceneID="1081" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1081" ElementID="13" SceneID="1081" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey’s </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> emerges out of the darkness. The passenger’s door opens then the driver’s door opens. Two figures move to the front of the truck, silhouetted by the bright headlights of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. The silhouettes are of sharp figures, first that of a lady in a short skirt business suit and heels and the other a man in a well tailored suit. There are five cars parked in a half circle. Three of the five cars are custom, shinny rims and exotic paint jobs, fancy doors and of course loud speakers. The occupants of the cars start to get out. The frame freezes introducing each man as he steps out of his car. The first is BUNS 29, his name types on the screen next to his frozen image. Buns, a thug through and through. He's wearing </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">saggy</Text>
      <Text> jeans and timberlands. His LA Dodgers hat sits sideways on his head. He's smoking a blunt looking none to pleased. Next is BIG FOLKS 33, his name types on the screen next to his frozen image. Big Folks is a big African-American man. He has gold fronts and a Newport hanging off his lips. Dressed in his white T-shirt and shaggy jeans, his big gold chain hangs down to his belt. Next is </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">PEPE</Text>
      <Text>` 37, his name types on the screen next to his frozen image. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Pepe</Text>
      <Text>` is a Mexican street gang member complete with the 19th Street Gang tattoo on his forehead. He’s dressed all in blue, his arms and neck covered in tattoos too. Next is </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">NICKY</Text>
      <Text> 29, his name types on the screen next to his frozen image. A Mexican man, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Nicky</Text>
      <Text> wears his Dicky’s work pants and Chuck Tailors with his dark </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">loc’ed</Text>
      <Text> out shades. He’s representing the 23rd Street crew. One of the many Mexican Mafia satellite units. The last to be introduced is different from all the rest. His name types on the screen next to his frozen image. Older and more mature, he appears as though he could, should be in Tara’s crew. JOHN 49 is dress in a blazer, golf shirt and Docker pants. He’s an African-American man, salt and pepper hair and a sophistication about him. He stands twirling his huge black onyx pinky ring. Shawntey steps forward into the light. He has a nickel plated .45 in his belt. All of the guys there except John start to laugh. Shawntey is confused, not sure what or where the joke is. Buns centers the laughter. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="1806" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="38" SceneID="1081" Start="1806" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="256" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="140" SceneID="1081" Start="256" Length="27"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="288" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="141" SceneID="1081" Start="288" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="319" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="142" SceneID="1081" Start="319" Length="18"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="397" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="143" SceneID="1081" Start="397" Length="21"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="928" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="105" SceneID="1081" Start="928" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="1122" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="144" SceneID="1081" Start="1122" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="1360" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1082" ElementID="145" SceneID="1081" Start="1360" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>BUNS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1083" ElementID="22" SceneID="1081" Start="0" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> you coming from, church? You and the doctor down there... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(looks to John) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">...on</Text>
      <Text> your way to the driving range? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Buns is tickled by his own joke, all but John again are fill with laughter at Bun’s clowning. Shawntey looks back to the other silhouetted figure. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1088" ElementID="2" SceneID="1081" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>HEY! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The young men stop laughing, their attention drawn back to the strong woman’s voice. Tara steps next to Shawntey into the light. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This was only a courtesy. It’s going down with or without you. It's a new day and a new way of doing business. If you want to do business with us, then you look and act the part. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(directly addresses Buns) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Dress like a man instead of a boy and you won't be so noticeable. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>All of the jokes and smiles fall from everyone’s face. John has a little smile form on his. Buns’ smile has turn to stone, upset that she has disrespected him. The others look on, to see if Buns will test. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>BUNS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What! </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Fuck</Text>
      <Text> you bitch. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(turning to the other guys) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yo </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> this bitch. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">gonna</Text>
      <Text> let some bitch come in here and tells us it’s a new </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">muthafuckn</Text>
      <Text> day? Shawntey what the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> you on with this bitch? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Getting no response from his peers, Buns continues. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>BUNS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Fuck</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">niggas</Text>
      <Text>. Bitch </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">gon</Text>
      <Text> call us here, make us wait then tell me there's a new day and a new way. I got my way bitch, it ain’t broke. You ain’t the only one ‘round with the flame </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">yayo</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Fuck</Text>
      <Text> you and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> this. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Na</Text>
      <Text> What! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara doesn't hesitate. She snatches the .45 from Shawntey's belt. Walking right over to Buns. She puts the gun to his forehead. Buns isn't scared in the least bit. He blows her a kiss. Tara looks down the slide of the gun. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="40" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1103" ElementID="146" SceneID="1081" Start="40" Length="3"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION the slide goes back and the shell flies from the ejector port. Tara's eyes are cold and all business. At the truck the back door flies open and Cassidy comes out with the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">GSG</Text>
      <Text> 5 </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">HK</Text>
      <Text> pointed at the entire meeting. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="159" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1104" ElementID="16" SceneID="1081" Start="159" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="186" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1104" ElementID="149" SceneID="1081" Start="186" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION Buns' body falls. The rest of the men look on stun. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(screaming) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Does anyone else have a problem with my clothes? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Silence. Tara not looking back holds the gun out, Shawntey comes up and takes it putting it back into his belt. Tara goes back to her soft feminine demeanor. She makes a motion to the truck. Xiomare comes out of the truck with a small wooden box. She steps to each guy to give them a sample as well as a taste if they want it. Xiomare steps over Buns’ dead body to get at the first man. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="227" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1109" ElementID="147" SceneID="1081" Start="227" Length="18"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Gentlemen, please have a little sample and a taste if you like. We can offer this to you at 12K per and 10K if you order more then 20. Shawntey will be your contact, any questions or concerns you bring it to him. Glad to have met you all. Have a very good evening. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare has a way with men and has them all smiling as she passes out the goodies. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Now finished with her passing out of the samples Xiomare heads back to the truck. Cassidy still has her assault weapon trained on the meeting. Tara moves back to the truck as well. Shawntey is the last to move. He makes eye contact with everyone giving them all a head nod. He spins on his heels and is back at the truck as well. Cassidy does not change position. The truck backs away from the meeting back into the darkness. Cassidy still with them in her sights. After the truck is out of sight the men all get in their cars and pull away leaving Buns’ body and car there. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="60" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="53" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. SHAWNTEY’S </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SUV</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1114" ElementID="13" SceneID="1114" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1114" ElementID="16" SceneID="1114" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1114" ElementID="2" SceneID="1114" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1114" ElementID="1" SceneID="1114" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1114" ElementID="104" SceneID="1114" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="7" ParagraphID="1114" ElementID="45" SceneID="1114" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> speeds away from the meeting. All are feeling the charge of the moment, stun not saying a word. All but Cassidy and Shawntey look shocked. Tara sits stone face, gazing straight ahead, eyes not focused. There’s a speck of blood on her forehead. She rubs her head getting blood on her hand. She pulls down the cosmetic mirror on the visor. She sees the blood, wipes it off and stares at herself in the mirror. THE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>SHOT ZOOMS into her looking at herself. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="61" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="54" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. TALKING HEADS </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">- DAY</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1118" ElementID="2" SceneID="1118" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1118" ElementID="90" SceneID="1118" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1118" ElementID="150" SceneID="1118" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>MUSIC MONTAGE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is talking on the phone full screen. A second window slides Tara's to the side, it's Shawntey. Now there are two screens. He’s talking on the phone, another window slides to the bottom of the frame, now Tara, Shawntey and Big Folk talking on the phone. He’s ordering up some goods. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Pepe</Text>
      <Text>` now owns a frame that replaces Tara in the screen mix. His frame fills the bottom, Big Folk and Shawntey occupy the top two screens. John calls next. His screen comes in on top. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Nicky’s</Text>
      <Text> screen comes in from the left. He pushes Shawntey’s screen to the bottom. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="426" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1120" ElementID="38" SceneID="1118" Start="426" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="90" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1120" ElementID="1" SceneID="1118" Start="90" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="227" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1120" ElementID="105" SceneID="1118" Start="227" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="287" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1120" ElementID="144" SceneID="1118" Start="287" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="471" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1120" ElementID="145" SceneID="1118" Start="471" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Two men that we have not seen before share the screen, pushing </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Nicky</Text>
      <Text> and Shawntey out. They are talking and they don’t look happy. Vincent slides in the bottom of the frame.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (SUBTITLE) </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1122" ElementID="23" SceneID="1118" Start="0" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>In the head, huh? * </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>All of the frames are replaced with the cell that Mr. Diaz * gave Tara. The cell has a picture message of a computer * screen. The screen has the address of a parking garage. Then there is another picture message that takes up another screen of the frame. The final picture message comes through. This message reads the time, 1 am. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="50" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1124" ElementID="8" SceneID="1118" Start="50" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>  SCREEN WIPE TO:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="62" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="54" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">GTS</Text>
      <Text> UNLIMITED FIREARMS RANGE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1126" ElementID="16" SceneID="1126" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1126" ElementID="1" SceneID="1126" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1126" ElementID="2" SceneID="1126" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1126" ElementID="13" SceneID="1126" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1126" ElementID="9" SceneID="1126" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1126" ElementID="44" SceneID="1126" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1126" ElementID="151" SceneID="1126" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies line up at the range. Cassidy paces behind them as they practice their marksmanship. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CAMERA SWIPE TO:  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="63" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="54" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. ROOFTOP PARKING LOT - NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Mr. Diaz lean on the side of the transportation van. Mr. Diaz puffs on a cigar. He takes another out of his jacket pocket and offers it to Tara. She excepts not one to back down or take a short. Mr. Diaz pulls out his gold lighter and gives her a light. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1130" ElementID="8" SceneID="1129" Start="9" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1130" ElementID="2" SceneID="1129" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="42" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1130" ElementID="152" SceneID="1129" Start="42" Length="18"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="80" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1130" ElementID="129" SceneID="1129" Start="80" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="227" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1130" ElementID="153" SceneID="1129" Start="227" Length="12"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A couple of other guys are off loading two huge crates of the “stuff” moving it to Tara’s transport van. A couple men guard the elevator, a couple more the entrance leading up to the meeting. Tara looks like a million bucks, dressed to the floor. Kim is with her. Her full sexy is on display, no longer the shrinking violet. She has a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">iPad</Text>
      <Text> and is all about the numbers. She’s asking the guys questions as they move the crates. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="39" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1131" ElementID="154" SceneID="1129" Start="39" Length="15"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="105" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1131" ElementID="155" SceneID="1129" Start="105" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="247" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1131" ElementID="9" SceneID="1129" Start="247" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="335" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1131" ElementID="156" SceneID="1129" Start="335" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>SCREEN WIPE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="64" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="55" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare leads Shawntey into the office. She’s carrying a briefcase that she got from one of her pick ups. Kim and Cassidy are sitting on the couch in front of the plasma. They join everyone at Tara’s desk. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1134" ElementID="13" SceneID="1133" Start="0" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="14" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1134" ElementID="1" SceneID="1133" Start="14" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="163" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1134" ElementID="106" SceneID="1133" Start="163" Length="6"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara doesn’t see anything on Xiomare and Shawntey’s face to give clues on how the meeting went. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (SUBTITLE) </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1136" ElementID="2" SceneID="1133" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So... How did it go. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare swings the briefcase to the desk and opens it. She turns the case around to Tara. A huge smile spreads across everyone’s face. Xiomare starts to take the money out of the case and pile it on the table. Everyone begins to hug knowing where this endeavor is headed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Returning to the money which digitally grows in size, amount, height, in every way possible. The commercial endeavor that Tara and her crew have realized is paying. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="65" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="55" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. BANK - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> pulls to the curb in front. Kim steps out of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> carrying a duffle bag followed by Cassidy, who has her head on a swivel like the well-trained soldier she is. She also has a ear piece in her ear. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1141" ElementID="104" SceneID="1140" Start="0" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="40" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1141" ElementID="9" SceneID="1140" Start="40" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="74" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1141" ElementID="157" SceneID="1140" Start="74" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="99" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1141" ElementID="16" SceneID="1140" Start="99" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="188" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1141" ElementID="158" SceneID="1140" Start="188" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="66" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="55" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY’S </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SUV</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1142" ElementID="1" SceneID="1142" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>There’s a radio sitting on Shawntey’s lap. He also has an ear piece in his ear. They have their stuff together. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="8" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1143" ElementID="159" SceneID="1142" Start="8" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="55" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1143" ElementID="160" SceneID="1142" Start="55" Length="12"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="67" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="55" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. BANK</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> LOBBY</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1144" ElementID="161" SceneID="1144" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1144" ElementID="16" SceneID="1144" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON THE CONTENTS OF THE DUFFLE BAG. Kim is showing JAKE WILLIAMSON 50 what’s in the bag. He looks up from the bag nervously and points to his office in the rear of the bank. He checks Kim and Cassidy out as they walk by. Then he nervously looks around the lobby. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="41" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1145" ElementID="9" SceneID="1144" Start="41" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="56" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1145" ElementID="162" SceneID="1144" Start="56" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="68" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="56" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. SANTA MONICA PIER - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Marco Jr walk and play. It’s a beautiful day and all is right with the world. Marco Jr has a balloon and a big cotton candy. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1147" ElementID="2" SceneID="1146" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1147" ElementID="97" SceneID="1146" Start="9" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="100" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1147" ElementID="163" SceneID="1146" Start="100" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="116" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1147" ElementID="164" SceneID="1146" Start="116" Length="16"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>THE FRAME freezes and becomes a still picture. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1148" ElementID="165" SceneID="1146" Start="0" Length="45"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>SF/X TRANSITION TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="69" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="56" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. PRISON</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> CELL</Text>
      <Text> - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>In Marco Sr's prison cell he’s adding a couple new pictures to all sorts of Tara and Marco Jr doing everything under the sun. They’re at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Disneyland</Text>
      <Text>, Magic Mountain, and a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">NASCAR</Text>
      <Text> race. The pictures brings a smile, then a frown. The thought of not being there with them. He goes back to those he blames for this distance and he fumes. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="3" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1151" ElementID="5" SceneID="1150" Start="3" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="188" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1151" ElementID="166" SceneID="1150" Start="188" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="70" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="56" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. NEW YORK SECURITIES FIRM - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>TITLES: New York </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Kim shakes hands with a very senior looking ASSETS MANAGER 55. Tara and Kim look very much like high net worth clients. The greet is extra friendly. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1154" ElementID="2" SceneID="1152" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1154" ElementID="9" SceneID="1152" Start="9" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="53" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1154" ElementID="167" SceneID="1152" Start="53" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="71" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="56" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. SWITZERLAND SECURITIES FIRM - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>TITLES: Switzerland </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Kim dressed in winter clothes shake hands in the other office of this Swiss Securities firm. The MAN 45 greeting them steps to them with a great smile. He looks very happy to have their business. He is followed by a YOUNG WOMAN 30 that is carrying a tray with hot coffee. Kim smiles and Tara is all business. She doesn’t smile or take the coffee. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1157" ElementID="2" SceneID="1155" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1157" ElementID="9" SceneID="1155" Start="9" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="102" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1157" ElementID="168" SceneID="1155" Start="102" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="231" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1157" ElementID="169" SceneID="1155" Start="231" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="257" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1157" ElementID="170" SceneID="1155" Start="257" Length="22"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="72" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="56" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. NIGHT CLUB - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1158" ElementID="171" SceneID="1158" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare and Shawntey dance together. Them seem to be connecting. Shawntey pulls her close. Their tempo is much slower then the other dancers who all dance at a high tempo. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1159" ElementID="13" SceneID="1158" Start="0" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="12" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1159" ElementID="1" SceneID="1158" Start="12" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="73" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="56" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S NEW CONDO - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara stands at the stove flipping pancakes. Marco Jr sits at the table bathed in the morning sun waiting for his breakfast. He plays with his Hot Wheels at the table. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1161" ElementID="2" SceneID="1160" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="44" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1161" ElementID="7" SceneID="1160" Start="44" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="142" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1161" ElementID="172" SceneID="1160" Start="142" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="25" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1161" ElementID="173" SceneID="1160" Start="25" Length="17"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="74" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="57" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">EAST-SIDE</Text>
      <Text> HOUSE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare pulls up in a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> and gets out and moves to the house. She is looking business with her sexy edge. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1163" ElementID="13" SceneID="1162" Start="0" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="20" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1163" ElementID="104" SceneID="1162" Start="20" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="75" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="57" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">EAST-SIDE</Text>
      <Text> HOUSE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A YOUNG MAN 27 answers the door and moves back to the couch where he’s watching TV drinking a beer. He eyes Xiomare as she moves through the house. He returns to his TV and beer without a word. The house is lightly furnished but not looking lived in. Xiomare moves to the kitchen. She pulls up a false floor board where there are several kilos wrapped in brown butcher’s paper. Also in the secret compartment is two duffle bags. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1165" ElementID="174" SceneID="1164" Start="0" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="80" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1165" ElementID="98" SceneID="1164" Start="80" Length="2"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="92" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1165" ElementID="175" SceneID="1164" Start="92" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="108" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1165" ElementID="13" SceneID="1164" Start="108" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="294" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1165" ElementID="176" SceneID="1164" Start="294" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="330" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1165" ElementID="177" SceneID="1164" Start="330" Length="46"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="412" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1165" ElementID="178" SceneID="1164" Start="412" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON THE LABEL, it reads; For John. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="34" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1166" ElementID="38" SceneID="1164" Start="34" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare reaches in and grabs the bags and leaves the house. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="76" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="57" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. EAST-SIDE CAR WASH OFFICE- DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Vincent and is right hand man </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">FRANKIE</Text>
      <Text> 31 sit in the office. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Frankie</Text>
      <Text> is an excitable aggressive young man. He is visibly upset about something. He paces and rants about something. They are the only big-time dealers that didn't show up at Tara's big meeting. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1169" ElementID="23" SceneID="1168" Start="0" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="30" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1169" ElementID="179" SceneID="1168" Start="30" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION on one side of the FRAME </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Frankie</Text>
      <Text> rants. On the other side of the FRAME Vincent sits calmly listening to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Frankie</Text>
      <Text>. Vincent smokes a big cigar almost motionless. He’s calm, calculating and cunning. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="143" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1170" ElementID="129" SceneID="1168" Start="143" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="77" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="57" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. PRISON VISITOR'S ROOM - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1171" ElementID="38" SceneID="1171" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The Unseen Man with the onyx pinky ring sits at the window talking and Marco listens. Marco stays abreast of the happenings. There’s always a way, this is Marco’s way of staying informed. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="71" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1172" ElementID="5" SceneID="1171" Start="71" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="24" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1172" ElementID="180" SceneID="1171" Start="24" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="78" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="57" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. BANK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">LOBBY </Text>
      <Text>- DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Kim comes in, greets Jake Williamson. This time Xiomare and Cassidy are with her and they both have two duffle bags. This brings a double raised eyebrow look from the banker. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1174" ElementID="9" SceneID="1173" Start="0" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="21" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1174" ElementID="162" SceneID="1173" Start="21" Length="15"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="48" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1174" ElementID="13" SceneID="1173" Start="48" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="60" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1174" ElementID="16" SceneID="1173" Start="60" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="104" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1174" ElementID="181" SceneID="1173" Start="104" Length="12"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="79" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="58" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. BANK - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1175" ElementID="151" SceneID="1175" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1175" ElementID="104" SceneID="1175" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A couple of men watch Kim, Xiomare and Cassidy from an unidentified car. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="22" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1176" ElementID="9" SceneID="1175" Start="22" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="27" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1176" ElementID="13" SceneID="1175" Start="27" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="39" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1176" ElementID="16" SceneID="1175" Start="39" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="55" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1176" ElementID="182" SceneID="1175" Start="55" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1176" ElementID="183" SceneID="1175" Start="0" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The women are coming out of the bank after their drop-off. A third man sits in the back seat, he leans on the front seat pointing out the ladies. The two unidentified men in the front seat step from their car and walk towards the ladies coming out of the bank. The man from the back seat gets out and moves to the driver’s seat. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION, the two men move towards the ladies. They have guns in their hands that are down by their sides as they walk. Cassidy and Xiomare get in the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. Kim is the last to get in. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN REAL-TIME, one of the men puts the gun to Kim’s side. The other man continues to the passenger’s side door and points the gun at Shawntey who’s caught totally off guard, along with Cassidy. They are all taking the ease of the success for granted. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Very quickly the car they came in pulls up fast next to the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. Kim is lead to the car and pushed in the back seat. One of the unidentified man slides in next to her. The other moves to the passenger’s door, his gun still aimed at Shawntey and the others. The kidnappers speed away into downtown traffic </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>END OF MUSIC MONTAGE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="80" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 6/8" Page="58" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. TARA’S BLACK JAGUAR - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1182" ElementID="90" SceneID="1182" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1182" ElementID="48" SceneID="1182" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara gets a call on her cell, she looks at the phone before answering, its a private call. She answers it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1184" ElementID="2" SceneID="1182" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey you. What’s happening?  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> twenty dollar call. These guards got a great hustle over here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You need more money in your commissary? Cause I can... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>NO I don’t care about that. I call to tell you to be careful. I’m hearing all kinds of stuff. There maybe some people you can’t see in your mirrors. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara can understands talking on monitored phones. She tries to comfort Marco’s concerns. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m looking in my mirrors. I see them and we </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">have’em</Text>
      <Text> covered. We’re nearly home baby. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (O.S.)  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(yelling) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey, listen to me. Be careful the test is coming. If it gets crazy use what you know. Help is there if you need it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re good. I think that we’re close enough to him to take him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m not sure of the other...  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is interrupted by another call. She looks at the cell * again. This caller she knows.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Speak of the devil. I got to take this call baby. Call me later on the other line.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (O.S.)  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I love you baby. Be careful! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I will. Love you too.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara switches over to the other line. Her disposition is sunny having talked to her love. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s up Shawntey, everything good? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No we got a big </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> problem. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where are you? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>On my way to pick Marco up from his grandmother... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Fuck</Text>
      <Text> that go straight to the office and stay in your mirrors. I’m not sure what we’re dealing with. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(looking worried) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hangs up the phone and looks immediately into all of her mirrors. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shit</Text>
      <Text>! Here we go. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="81" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="60" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara comes into the office walking fast, eyes wide open both physically and literally. Xiomare and Shawntey sit on the couch in silence. Cassidy paces with an assault weapon in her hand. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="87" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1227" ElementID="13" SceneID="1226" Start="87" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="137" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1227" ElementID="16" SceneID="1226" Start="137" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="159" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1227" ElementID="184" SceneID="1226" Start="159" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1228" ElementID="2" SceneID="1226" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK what’s going on? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The group moves slowly to the desk in front of Tara. She takes off her hat and sits behind the desk. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1231" ElementID="1" SceneID="1226" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Kim got snatched in front of the bank. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara rises to her feet very quickly. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>WHAT! How could that be Cassidy? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What the hell was you doing </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Shawntey? Mr. Streets! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>They knew that we were going to be there and they got up on us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK, we’ll deal with all that later. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where are we on finding her. You make some calls? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I did and no one knows anything. I think we have to wait for them to call us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara’s jaws clenches with anger. She falls back into her big leather chair. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="82" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 5/8" Page="61" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Pizza boxes, empty liters of soda, bottled water, and a fifth of J &amp;amp; B Scotch liter the office. The crew all look concerned and worried. Tara sits behind her desk. Her cell rings</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1248" ElementID="185" SceneID="1247" Start="0" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="13" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1248" ElementID="186" SceneID="1247" Start="13" Length="20"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="35" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1248" ElementID="187" SceneID="1247" Start="35" Length="13"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="54" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1248" ElementID="188" SceneID="1247" Start="54" Length="23"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="168" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1248" ElementID="90" SceneID="1247" Start="168" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNSEEN MAN (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Follow the money. It will tell you what you need to know. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The call goes dead before Tara can say anything. Her cell being on vibrate has kept the entire crew from being in on her call. She’s able to have that moment and it not break the tension of the room. Everyone is still waiting pensively for the call about Kim. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The phone rings breaking that deafening silence. Tara stands up, the others in the office join her at the desk. Tara pushes the speaker button after checking to see if everyone is ready. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="4" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1252" ElementID="189" SceneID="1247" Start="4" Length="11"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1253" ElementID="2" SceneID="1247" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This is Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The voice on the other end of the phone has been electronically altered. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNKNOWN VOICE </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1256" ElementID="24" SceneID="1247" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>There’s always a price for blood. This business has rules and they must be followed. You took Buns and the price is your banker and $500K. Tomorrow you bring the money back to the pier. Same place you drop Buns. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>When do I get Kim back? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNKNOWN VOICE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>She’ll be there. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The phone line goes dead. Tara falls back in her seat. She takes a beat. She ponders her killing Buns. The decision that triggered this. She realizes that she shares the blame with these men. She’s a little shaken by the thought. Tara still maintains her head for the business though not sounding cold. Her steadiness coming from the help and inside information that the others aren’t privy to. Her calmness soothes the others that have only their wits to rely on. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="97" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1262" ElementID="22" SceneID="1247" Start="97" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK, OK, we need to ah... We need to check all of our houses. We need to check everything because someone is watching us. Be careful at home, In fact don’t go home. Cassidy,</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>Xiomare go to the east side stash house and grab everything and take it to the west side house. That one just opened. AH.. I’ll get the money for Kim. Shawntey and I will handle that in the morning. We’ll all stay here tonight. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy and Xiomare slowly leave the office. Shawntey stays. Tara sits back in her seat, deep in thought. She comes out of it reaching for the phone. She dials and awaits an answer. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey ma, I’ll be by tomorrow to get </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco. No, no everything is cool. We just had more to do then I thought. I’ll give you a call in the morning. Love you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hangs up the phone and returns to her position of thought. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="83" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="62" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY </Text>
      <Text>BLACK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SUV</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare and Cassidy riding in the black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. They turn the corner onto the block of the house. Cassidy sees the unmarked police car immediately. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="34" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1272" ElementID="104" SceneID="1271" Start="34" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="112" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1272" ElementID="190" SceneID="1271" Start="112" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1273" ElementID="16" SceneID="1271" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Damn are they sitting on us?  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1275" ElementID="13" SceneID="1271" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What do we do? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Drive around back, park with the</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>lights off, engine running. I’m going to come out the back. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cool. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="84" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="63" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. UNMARKED POLICE CAR</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> 1</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1281" ElementID="16" SceneID="1281" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1281" ElementID="104" SceneID="1281" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The silhouetted figure of a woman dressed in a business suit steps from the truck and heads to the door of the modest house. The </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> turns into the driveway and goes back the way it came. The officers look at each other. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNMARKED OFFICER #1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1283" ElementID="25" SceneID="1281" Start="0" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s that the landlord or the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>guy’s mother or something? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNMARKED OFFICER #2 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1285" ElementID="26" SceneID="1281" Start="0" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(chuckles) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t know. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Officer #2 is still looking through his binoculars. He’s trying to see the plate on the truck as it drives away. It’s a temporary plate. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1288" ElementID="29" SceneID="1281" Start="0" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="120" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1288" ElementID="191" SceneID="1281" Start="120" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNMARKED OFFICER #2 (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No luck on the plate. It’s a temp. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Why is he leaving her? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="85" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="63" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. EAST-SIDE STASH HOUSE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy walks to the door of the house. She knocks a few times. She can hear the loud music and smell the weed smoke. Another YOUNG MAN 25, peeks through the window of the door. He opens the door with a smile on his face. Cassidy starts into the house. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="126" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1293" ElementID="192" SceneID="1292" Start="126" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1294" ElementID="16" SceneID="1292" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Fuck</Text>
      <Text> you doing smiling at me. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>There’s </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> cops watching the house. Turn the damn music down, put the weed out and pay attention to the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> street. Wipe down everything and leave out of the back door. Shawntey will call you when it’s time. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy says the last of the orders over her shoulder. She moves to the false floor in the kitchen. She grabs a backpack off the floor and puts the plastic bricks from the false floor in the backpack. She takes the backpack filled with drugs and continues out the back door. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="110" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1297" ElementID="193" SceneID="1292" Start="110" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="148" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1297" ElementID="194" SceneID="1292" Start="148" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="86" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="64" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. EAST-SIDE STASH HOUSE BACKYARD - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1298" ElementID="13" SceneID="1298" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Now through the back door standing at the back gate, Cassidy kicks off her heels, scales the fence and walks across an open lot to the black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> sitting with it’s lights off. The young man stands in the doorway watching Cassidy, amazed. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="53" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1299" ElementID="16" SceneID="1298" Start="53" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="135" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1299" ElementID="104" SceneID="1298" Start="135" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="175" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1299" ElementID="195" SceneID="1298" Start="175" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="87" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="64" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY’S </Text>
      <Text>BLACK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SUV</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1300" ElementID="16" SceneID="1300" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy is in the passenger’s seat now as Xiomare drives. She talks into the earpiece that she’s wearing. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="77" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1301" ElementID="196" SceneID="1300" Start="77" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1302" ElementID="13" SceneID="1300" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea T, they was some plain clothes dudes sitting on the house. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where’s all this attention coming from?... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="88" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="64" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICES - NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hangs the phone up. She’s looking a bit wore by the circumstances. She looks up to Shawntey who’s standing on the other side of the desk. Shawntey looks a worried too. He falls back in her seat. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1306" ElementID="2" SceneID="1305" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="15" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1306" ElementID="197" SceneID="1305" Start="15" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1307" ElementID="1" SceneID="1305" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>When we started this you asked for a 18 month window. Its been almost five years. How much more money you need? I thinks its time. Walk away. Marco can get out as soon as two summers. You’ll have your family and more money then you can spend. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON TARA. Shawntey is making complete sense. Her eyes are down. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (O.S.) (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll run it for you, keep the money flowing for you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara’s eyes quickly snap up to Shawntey. She expression changing, realization washing over her. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="89" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="64" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. LONG BEACH PIER 79 - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1314" ElementID="198" SceneID="1314" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1314" ElementID="106" SceneID="1314" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1314" ElementID="199" SceneID="1314" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey’s </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> pulls up. They are the only vehicle around. Tara gets out of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> with a briefcase and is joined by Shawntey. A MASKED MAN walks in front of a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> that slowly creeps behind him. Tara and Shawntey exchange looks. The Masked Man, a gun now visible walks up to Tara and Shawntey. Another Masked Man gets out of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> and joins his partner. He too has a gun. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1315" ElementID="1" SceneID="1314" Start="0" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MASKED #1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1316" ElementID="295" SceneID="1314" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(points at the briefcase) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s our money? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1319" ElementID="2" SceneID="1314" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where’s Kim? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Masked Men #1 walks up to Tara looking her up and down. Getting in her face. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MASKED #1 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You are a good looking </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">muthafucka</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(snatches the briefcase from her hand) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>But you should get your ass back to school or house work or whatever the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> and leave this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> to the boys. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Masked Man #1 gives her a air kiss and walks past her and Shawntey, joined by Masked Man #2. They walk to the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1326" ElementID="35" SceneID="1314" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(yelling) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What about Kim? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MASKED #1 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>She’s parked over there. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Masked Man #1  points to a car parked in the distance. The two masked men get in the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> and pull off fast. Shawntey and Tara take off running towards the parked car. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="155" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1332" ElementID="200" SceneID="1314" Start="155" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="90" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="65" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. LONG BEACH PIER 79 - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1333" ElementID="2" SceneID="1333" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1333" ElementID="1" SceneID="1333" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1333" ElementID="200" SceneID="1333" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>They arrive at the car, look in the window and they both slide down the car crying. Kim is in the back seat shot in the chest, dead. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="91" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="65" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. OUTSIDE OF LONG BEACH PIER 79 - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy is sitting outside of the of the park on watch. She sees the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> come out fast. Then she speaks into her radio. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="69" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1336" ElementID="199" SceneID="1335" Start="69" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="113" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1336" ElementID="201" SceneID="1335" Start="113" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1337" ElementID="16" SceneID="1335" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yo, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> OK? ...(a beat) Hello, hello... </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> OK? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Stay with that car. Kim is dead. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy’s SUV pulls away fast. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="92" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="6/8" Page="66" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S NEW CONDO - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1343" ElementID="38" SceneID="1343" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is talking to someone that can’t be identified. She’s pacing trying to put everything together and figure the next move. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1345" ElementID="2" SceneID="1343" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I think that you are the only person that I can trust in this thing now. I’m getting close. We have them all in place and ready to show their asses. But this is no longer about Marco. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON TARA </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This is about Kim. I want the </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">muthafuckas</Text>
      <Text> that killed Kim.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Whatever we have to do. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is pacing,. She stops as if a thought just hit her. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I think we should move to the end. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m ready. Everyone is where they</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>should be right? What are we missing? Who are we missing? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is interrupted by a cell. She walks to the counter and grabs the cell. She shakes it at the unidentified man as if to say that here it is. She answers. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="70" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1356" ElementID="90" SceneID="1343" Start="70" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">what’cha</Text>
      <Text> got? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="93" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="66" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. POLICE STATION - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Two plain clothed police officers sit in the SUV from the night before. The passenger has the briefcase open. They both have huge smiles. They jump out and go into the building which now can be seen as a police station. Cassidy sits across the street talking into a cell. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1361" ElementID="16" SceneID="1359" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You ain’t going to believe who the </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> these dudes are! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="94" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="67" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S NEW CONDO - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A smile crosses Tara’s smile. She looks to the unidentified man and gives him a nod. The unidentified man takes a hit of his cigarette showing a huge onyx ring on the his pinky finger. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="16" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1365" ElementID="2" SceneID="1364" Start="16" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="89" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1365" ElementID="38" SceneID="1364" Start="89" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="125" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1365" ElementID="202" SceneID="1364" Start="125" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="143" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1365" ElementID="203" SceneID="1364" Start="143" Length="16"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="95" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="67" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. CEMETERY - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION Tara, Cassidy, Xiomare and Shawntey are walking towards their cars after the ceremony. They all look very upset. Tara hides her eyes behind her big dark sunglasses though tears roll down her face. Kim’s family also walks away from the site. They too are emotional. Everyone is dressed in the color of grieving, black. Xiomare walks next to Shawntey. She reaches out to Shawntey’s hand and they lock. Its a small undetachable thing to the others. But Shawntey and Xiomare are connecting. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="21" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1367" ElementID="16" SceneID="1366" Start="21" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="30" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1367" ElementID="13" SceneID="1366" Start="30" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="42" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1367" ElementID="1" SceneID="1366" Start="42" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="159" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1367" ElementID="204" SceneID="1366" Start="159" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CROSS DISSOLVE: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="96" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 4/8" Page="67" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. EAST-SIDE CAR WASH - OFFICE - NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON A GLASS TABLE, a shot glass comes down onto it. Also on the table is a couple of lines of white powder. Fingers come down onto the table with a straw and traces one of the lines, sucking up the drugs. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="78" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1370" ElementID="205" SceneID="1369" Start="78" Length="33"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="151" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1370" ElementID="206" SceneID="1369" Start="151" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey is getting smashed. Vincent sits behind his desk with a drink of his own. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Frankie</Text>
      <Text> is off to the side looking  like the enforcer.  </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="29" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1371" ElementID="23" SceneID="1369" Start="29" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="83" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1371" ElementID="179" SceneID="1369" Start="83" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="63" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1371" ElementID="207" SceneID="1369" Start="63" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Why this Shawntey, why be in our business if you don’t have to be. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>She can go be a model or do </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">flix</Text>
      <Text> I give a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>. But she needs to leave this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> to the gladiators. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Vincent gets up and wonders around to the front of the desk. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What makes her think that she got a place at our table. Marco got a pass because he was catering to that country club crowd. And of course because he had you on his team. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Vincent Moves around the desk and sits on the corner in front of Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You got her think we’ve been some pussies about this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>. If that weren't Marco’s wife how long would this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> be going on? A bunch of woman making that kind of money and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>. And the thing with Buns, what the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> Shawntey? YOU know you have to come to the table before you can draw blood. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shit</Text>
      <Text> she brought this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> on herself. Blood in, blood out. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The whole speech Shawntey is just listening. He clears his nose as he does. He doesn’t outwardly agree but the feelings behind his face are clearly in that same place. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1382" ElementID="1" SceneID="1369" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>She told me that she would bail when Marco gets out then give the connect to me. Me with that connect, it’s going to be a whole different ball-game. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Vincent listens with a twisted lip. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>If Marco didn’t give you the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> connect when he went away, what makes you think that she’s going to? All I’m saying is, let me help you help me! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Finally we can se the entire room. Xiomare is sitting next to Shawntey holding his hand. They have made their relationship public. Shawntey’s head is down. He’s not fully on-board with the plot. Xiomare looks to Vincent. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="195" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1387" ElementID="13" SceneID="1369" Start="195" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>CLOSE ON XIOMARE. She smiles at Vincent. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>CLOSE ON VINCENT. He smiles back at Xiomare. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text/>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text/>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>TITLES OVER BLACK SCREEN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>INMATE #</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">35728'S</Text>
      <Text> MARCO REED SR. * </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>RELEASE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>ONE MONTH </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="97" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="69" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. PRISON VISITOR’S ROOM- DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara sits in front of the glass that separates the cons from the world. She and Marco just look at each other. Marco’s expression changes as he realizes that there is a weight, a sadness to Tara. She lowers her head then begins to collect * her stuff to leave. She stands. Marco just watches. Tara turns back to the glass, picks up the phone. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1399" ElementID="2" SceneID="1397" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Everything is in place. We have eyes on them. I’m going to see them all for Kim. I owe her that. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1401" ElementID="5" SceneID="1397" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Be careful with him. He’s been playing both sides a long time. He may have another guy we can’t see. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t want you blind-sided. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>They should worry about me now! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara kisses her hand then touches the glass and hangs up the phone. Tara leaves. Marco’s face fills with concern. He let's escape a rye little smile though. Tara’s strength is impressive. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="98" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 3/8" Page="69" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. REED HOLDINGS INC. - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1408" ElementID="104" SceneID="1408" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>There are three cars in the parking lot at the end of this work day. Cassidy leans up against a plain </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> waiting on something or someone. Tara exits the building looking like a million dollars. She sees Cassidy and slows her step. She looks around not knowing what to expect. She steps over to Cassidy. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="96" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1409" ElementID="208" SceneID="1408" Start="96" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1410" ElementID="16" SceneID="1408" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What you expecting? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy looks as if she knows a secret. She has a rye smile. Tara stiffens looking Cassidy in the eyes. The both start laughing. Tara almost relieved that she doesn’t have to pretend anymore and Cassidy realizing that she hasn’t misinterpreted anything. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I know killers. The ones that enjoy the killing, seeing others in pain. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I served with a bunch of them. Their eyes are like doll’s eyes, lifeless, soulless. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON CASSIDY. See looks into Tara’s eyes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I look in your eyes and I see somebody not sleeping at night, somebody reliving choices. That’s not how those killers I served with lived. They </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> sleep like babies, ever having a second thought. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara looks Cassidy in the eyes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1420" ElementID="2" SceneID="1408" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cassidy I got... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You don’t have to lie to me. I know you working angle. Calls you think no one sees, reactions that don’t fit. I see you. I just wanted you to know I’m with you. I got more money </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">the</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">a</Text>
      <Text> my father made in his life. I owe you the new life that I have, the things I’ve done for my family. I bought my father a 87 Mustang convertible and paid his house off. I made my piece with death and the price of it when I landed in country. So I ain’t scared of nothing. I know everything ain’t as it seems. I see them </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">partnering</Text>
      <Text> off. I just wanted you to know I’m with you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON TARA. She gives Cassidy an approving nod. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy does the same. Tara lowers her sunglasses that she put on her forehead to look into Cassidy’s eyes. Both Cassidy and Tara both move to their </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUVs</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="39" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1426" ElementID="209" SceneID="1408" Start="39" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>From a distance someone looks on at this meeting. The FRAME freezes a couple of times as though someone is taking pictures. Cassidy and Tara’s trucks drive away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="99" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 3/8" Page="71" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. RESTAURANT - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1428" ElementID="102" SceneID="1428" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The plain clothes officers that took Tara’s $500K sit at a table on the same side meeting with someone yet unseen. They speak in low tones. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>OFFICER #1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1430" ElementID="28" SceneID="1428" Start="0" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>So you saying they got 52 joints over there right now. Plus the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> that came out of the old house. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Fuck</Text>
      <Text> it might be almost 100 joints over there huh? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Officer #1 looks around, he waves the waitress over. The waiter brings over another glass of the same, the three fingers of brown liquor. The waitress sits one of the glasses in front of the person sitting across from the officers. Xiomare grabs the drink and takes a sip. Officer #1 remembers something. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNMARKED OFFICER #1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1433" ElementID="25" SceneID="1428" Start="0" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Before I forget...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>He slides an envelop filled in the shape of money across the table. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>UNMARKED OFFICER #2 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1436" ElementID="26" SceneID="1428" Start="0" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Vince says that you done good. There is way more if we can make this other thing happen. Now tell me about the stash house. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare takes the cash, slides it down to her lap then looks in it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1439" ElementID="13" SceneID="1428" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Nice, nice... Well the other house is right off Raven. And... ain’t nobody sitting on it. Once they bring the ones at the office over there, you could be right there? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(Takes a couple of swallows of her drink) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cassidy is the only one that knows anything about guns. Shawntey is with me, and Tara, that bitch wants to walk away. She’s going to fold at any moment. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(Takes another swallow of her drink) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This thing is Shawntey’s by right anyway. He wants 25 bricks. No </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> that. Tell Vincent we want to be his partners. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>OFFICER #2 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1445" ElementID="29" SceneID="1428" Start="0" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Partner! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare downs the last of his three finger drink. She’s feeling the call of nature. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea partners. What you got without us? I’ll be back, got to go to the lady’s room. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare staggers towards the bathroom. Before she gets to the bathroom, she passes John sitting with a LOVELY LADY friend. He notices Xiomare but she doesn’t see him. John looks down to the booth Xiomare was sitting at. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="83" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1450" ElementID="38" SceneID="1428" Start="83" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="100" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 1/8" Page="72" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. TARA REED’S NEW CONDO - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1451" ElementID="7" SceneID="1451" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is chilling in the TV room of her very nice condo. Marco Jr is playing video games in front of her. Tara is holding a letter, worn from being read more then a few times. She opens the it. It’s dated 7.17.07 (a year and a half earlier). Tara’s eyes are teary. The first line reads: </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="76" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1452" ElementID="210" SceneID="1451" Start="76" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="121" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1452" ElementID="211" SceneID="1451" Start="121" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>My dearest love, my heart’s desire... At the bottom of the letter we can read: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Love You Always. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is in the middle of writing a letter back to Marco. The phone rings. Tara shakes her tears and answers it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1457" ElementID="2" SceneID="1451" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hello </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey momma, you good? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m good, got a lot on my plate. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Sitting here thinking about Kim and.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re free to choose our actions. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re not free to choose the consequences of our actions. You made a call, what happened</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>happened. You shut down all challengers right off the top. None of us had to fight because you put yourself in the fight from the beginning. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Thanks Cass. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1469" ElementID="16" SceneID="1451" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Leaders lead. Don’t look backwards. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You and me will be better for it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m going to go. I’ll talk to you </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">in</Text>
      <Text> the morning. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">babygirl</Text>
      <Text>. Sleep safe. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara hangs up. The weight of what’s happened to Kim, Marco not being there has her weary. Tara sits thinking. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="101" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="73" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. TARA REED’S NEW CONDO - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1478" ElementID="16" SceneID="1478" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON ASSAULT WEAPON ON SOMEONE’S LAP Cassidy sits in a black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> in front of Tara’s building with the automatic weapon on her lap. She looks to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">iPad</Text>
      <Text> and the e- book she’s reading, The Seven Habits of Highly Effective People. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1479" ElementID="184" SceneID="1478" Start="9" Length="14"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="59" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1479" ElementID="212" SceneID="1478" Start="59" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="148" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1479" ElementID="156" SceneID="1478" Start="148" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="184" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1479" ElementID="213" SceneID="1478" Start="184" Length="43"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="102" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4 5/8" Page="73" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara, Cassidy, and Xiomare sit on the couch looking at the evening news on the plasma. Everyone has their fine clothes on, except for Cassidy. She has on a black leather blazer, a mock neck sweater and driving gloves. This is her Black Panther look. The reporter is reporting on the breaking news. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="79" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1482" ElementID="214" SceneID="1481" Start="79" Length="6"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>NEWS REPORTER </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1483" ElementID="30" SceneID="1481" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Again breaking news. The FBI have formed a task force for the international drug cartels that have set up on both sides of the Mexican border. The FBI say there’s a surge of cocaine availability do</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>to new cartel leadership in the</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Narco</Text>
      <Text> States and the new import channels by their agents here in the States. Special Agent in Charge </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Edwards T. Simms took questions at Los Angeles FBI Field Offices. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>SPECIAL AGENT IN CHARGE SIMMS 52 stands in front of a bank of </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">mics</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SPECIAL AGENT IN CHARGE SIMMS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1487" ElementID="31" SceneID="1481" Start="0" Length="29"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re determined to put a stop to the trafficking that seems to have spiked in the last few years. The traffickers have used technology and new methods to pursue their ends and we’ve been vested with methods of our own by the Attorney </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>General to stop them cool. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The reports all roar trying to get their questions in. Tara and crew watch with serious faces. Tara looks at her watch a couple of times. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare</Text>
      <Text> looks as though she has swallowed the canary. Tara brings everybody back from the trance. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SPECIAL AGENT IN CHARGE SIMMS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Much like the many successful terrorist investigations tracking the money leads to results. I’ll take a few questions. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(fades) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> comes in clearing his nose as if he just had a line of coke. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1495" ElementID="2" SceneID="1481" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re all here. I guess we can start now. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(looking at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text>) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>OK everyone knows what to do, where to go right? Close the house down and bring the product back here. We’ll give it a couple of days then</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>figure out where the next spot will be. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY</Text>
      <Text> ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1499" ElementID="1" SceneID="1481" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What do you need from me? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You sit this one out. The ladies will take care of it. I have Cassidy if something goes wrong. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(with a twisted lip) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It sounds like you coming down with something. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> has the sniffles like he has a cold or a growing taste for coke. The ladies join them at the desk. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m good, taking the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Robitussin</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara does a double take as thought she’s surprised by the lame excuse. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We have our biggest delivery coming in the middle of some serious heat right now. I’ve been thinking of cancelling it until we get this straight. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare’s face tightens hoping that she doesn’t. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>But I made the order and I can’t contact Mr. Diaz. So I guess we’re going to have to make it work. But this time we need everybody. No chances. Everyone on their toes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara makes eye contact with everyone stressing the importance. She seems like she is thinking if she should finish her thought. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I ah... I’ve been thinking about this and I (a beat) think this our last turn too. I asked you guys for 18 months and you gave me nearly five years. I don’t need anything else from this thing. Marco is getting out soon. I have enough money for us. We move the last of this stuff and see these jokers about Kim and I’m gone. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON XIOMARE. She cuts her eyes to Shawntey. She doesn’t look happy at all. She slightly raises her eyebrows. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON SHAWNTEY. He looks like a dear caught in the headlights. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ah Tara... when we started you said once you decided to step away... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Shawn I think this is best for all of us. How much more money you need? Walk away Shawn. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare</Text>
      <Text> claps her hands together. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">XIOMARE</Text>
      <Text> JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1525" ElementID="13" SceneID="1481" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Aight</Text>
      <Text> then let’s celebrate. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey’s</Text>
      <Text> head snaps to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare</Text>
      <Text>. He looks confused by her comment. Cassidy is aware of the eye play between </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare</Text>
      <Text> and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">XIOMARE</Text>
      <Text> JAMES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I think I speak for everybody here when I say we’re thankful to sharing this opportunity with us. We all walk away from this with the world open to us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Xiomare</Text>
      <Text> looks around at Cassidy and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text>. Both are nodding in agreement. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Thank you </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cio</Text>
      <Text>. I appreciate that. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">XIOMARE</Text>
      <Text> JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Now let’s go play, rest our minds and just wild out. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara shakes her head not wanting to hang out. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I good on that </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Cio</Text>
      <Text> you guys... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">XIOMARE</Text>
      <Text> JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Come on T, you need it like the rest of us. Come kick it with the girls. Spend some of that money. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare looks over to Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Sorry Shawn. With the girls and </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy chimes in. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1546" ElementID="16" SceneID="1481" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let’s do this thing T. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m not feeling like playing. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> go ahead. I’m </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">gonna</Text>
      <Text> chill and... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>T, let it go. This would be a good thing for you, for all of us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara still not feeling it, asks halfheartedly. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where you talking about going? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Vegas. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies turn to Shawntey who they thought wasn’t in the conversation. All eyes on him now. After a beat, all the ladies agree in unison. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      </UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Come on T, we all could use a little play time. I feel as bad as the rest about Kim. But as you said, we’re almost done so let’s let our hair down some and hang out. Hell we’re rich. Let’s act like it a little bit. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara succumbs to peer pressure. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Aight</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">ya’ll</Text>
      <Text>. Let’s it. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies in unison cheer. The boss is on board. Xiomare and Shawntey share a look. This is the look of a bond. These two are feeling each other but very much still on the low in this circle. Cassidy pulls Shawntey to the side breaking his gaze at Xiomare. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Look dog, I need your opinion on a few pieces that I just came up on. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy leads Shawntey over to the closet. She opens it. * Shawntey isn’t paying attention. His attention is back at * Xiomare standing at Tara’s desk. Cassidy pulls out a blue * duffle bag. She pulls out a sawed-off </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">12-gauge</Text>
      <Text> shotgun and a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Beretta</Text>
      <Text> .45. She hands Shawntey the shotgun. He looks down the breach. He racks it a few times, feeling the action. He pulls the trigger. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="217" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1567" ElementID="215" SceneID="1481" Start="217" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="240" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1567" ElementID="216" SceneID="1481" Start="240" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="170" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1567" ElementID="217" SceneID="1481" Start="170" Length="18"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This one is straight. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy takes the gauge and hands him the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Beretta</Text>
      <Text>. Again Shawntey puts the gun through the paces, looking down the barrel, feeling the slide and pulling the trigger. He hands that one back to Cassidy too. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Both them joints good. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cool, cool. I’m glad I didn’t trick </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">off</Text>
      <Text> my </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> money. I thought that the gauge was a little slow in the action. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey walks back to Tara’s desk area. In the closet Cassidy puts the gauge and the handgun in a red duffle bag and some books in the blue duffle bag. She closes the door. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="97" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1576" ElementID="218" SceneID="1481" Start="97" Length="16"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="103" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="78" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">MCCARRAN</Text>
      <Text> INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1577" ElementID="16" SceneID="1577" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1577" ElementID="1" SceneID="1577" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1577" ElementID="13" SceneID="1577" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara leads her crew off of the private jet that brought them to Las Vegas. Cassidy follows Tara, then comes Xiomare and Shawntey. Xiomare and Shawntey are holding hands. Their relationship has blossomed. They all pile into an awaiting limo. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1578" ElementID="2" SceneID="1577" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="31" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1578" ElementID="219" SceneID="1577" Start="31" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="235" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1578" ElementID="220" SceneID="1577" Start="235" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="104" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="78" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. CASINO - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">CRAP</Text>
      <Text> TABLE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1579" ElementID="13" SceneID="1579" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1579" ElementID="2" SceneID="1579" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1579" ElementID="16" SceneID="1579" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A man moves through the casino. The place is jumping, all the action is in SLOW-MOTION. The man approaches the VIP tables where the ladies are doing their thing. Xiomare has the dice. Cassidy is feeling the liquor and the good-times. People have gather around this table of good times, beautiful ladies and the excitement of flowing money. Everyone smiles and laughs and consume more liquor. Tara stands behind it all, observant and still. All in black, Tara has her big </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Chanel</Text>
      <Text> sunglasses on. She looks very much like the big boss with her troops running amuck. The man observing the scene stops. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1580" ElementID="1" SceneID="1579" Start="0" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="286" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1580" ElementID="221" SceneID="1579" Start="286" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="325" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1580" ElementID="222" SceneID="1579" Start="325" Length="13"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="467" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1580" ElementID="223" SceneID="1579" Start="467" Length="21"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>It’s Shawntey looking on unnoticed. Through his drug infused hazed and confused mind, the vision that he sees is a collage of overlapping figures, blurring, some in real time others in slow-motion. Shawntey’s mind is playing tricks on him. The drugs and booze help to confuse what his mind see. He’s not digging this at all. He tries to shake this hallucination. Unable to shake it he steps back the way he came. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="105" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="78" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. CASINO - BAR - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey moves fast to the bar. When he lands he looks around and quickly pulls a vile of white powder from his pocket. He takes a couple of sniffs of the contents, tucks the vile then dials his cell. He looks around as the phone rings. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="80" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1583" ElementID="224" SceneID="1582" Start="80" Length="22"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="195" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1583" ElementID="90" SceneID="1582" Start="195" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hey baby. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1586" ElementID="1" SceneID="1582" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">wildin</Text>
      <Text> out, bringing a lot of attention to yourselves. Maybe </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">ya’ll</Text>
      <Text> should bring it down a bit. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where are you? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tell them they should bring it down then meet me out front. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="106" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="79" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. CASINO - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">CRAP</Text>
      <Text> TABLE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare closes her cell and moves close to Tara who’s sipping a water with a twist of lemon. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="19" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1593" ElementID="90" SceneID="1592" Start="19" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1594" ElementID="13" SceneID="1592" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>T, I’ll be back. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare walks off and Tara moves her dark sunglasses down on her nose. Cassidy moves close to her. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1597" ElementID="16" SceneID="1592" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s up with that? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1599" ElementID="2" SceneID="1592" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t know. Check it out. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy puts down her drink and walks after her slowly. Tara, now alone sips her water hidden behind her shades. The good times continues at the table. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="22" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1601" ElementID="225" SceneID="1592" Start="22" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="107" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="79" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. SHAWNTEY’S VEGAS SUITE - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1602" ElementID="13" SceneID="1602" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1602" ElementID="1" SceneID="1602" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A woman sits astride of a man. Their bodies are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">silhouettedby</Text>
      <Text> the big window in the background. The man and woman are in a wild fit of coitus. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="108" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="80" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. SHAWNTEY’S VEGAS SUITE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1605" ElementID="1" SceneID="1605" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1605" ElementID="13" SceneID="1605" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Now the man is behind the woman. The positioned changed but the lust and passion remain. The man reaches climax and slumps over the woman.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO:  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="109" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1" Page="80" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. SHAWNTEY’S VEGAS SUITE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">BIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1608" ElementID="1" SceneID="1608" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Siting on the edge of the bed, Shawntey has his back to the bed. His head is in his hands. He gets up and walks to the bathroom. He’s naked. Xiomare sleeps. Shawntey’s cell sits on the bed next to where he was sitting as if he was waiting on a call. Xiomare stirs as the cell rings. She leans forward to see who’s calling then looks towards the bathroom. She answers the phone speaking in low tones. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="244" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1609" ElementID="90" SceneID="1608" Start="244" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1610" ElementID="13" SceneID="1608" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s happening big boy. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s good ma? Where’s your boy at? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare looks towards the bathroom and sits up in the bed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>He had to make a run. He told me to take care of you. What you need? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I need to know what’s he </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">gonna</Text>
      <Text> do. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Xiomare looks again to towards the bathroom. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll make sure you get what you need </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">aight</Text>
      <Text>? I’m serious about that partnership thing. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Is this a me and you thing or is he in? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What difference does it make. I got you. That’s all that matters. I’ll </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">holla</Text>
      <Text> with a time and date. That makes us partners right? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare sits on the bed thinking. She too has the Tara/Marco rye smile on her face as she waits to hear that answer. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="110" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="81" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. VEGAS HOTEL HALLWAY - NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy leans against the wall of the hallway outside of Shawntey’s room. She takes out her cell and dials. She walks towards the elevators. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="92" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1629" ElementID="90" SceneID="1628" Start="92" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1630" ElementID="16" SceneID="1628" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea... they’re both in there doing </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">the</Text>
      <Text> nasty. Yea I know. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="111" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="81" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. TARA’S BLACK JAGUAR CONVERTIBLE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara rides in the black Jaguar. She’s as always looking like a million bucks. She drives down the side street around the corner from the stash house. She notices the unmarked police car watching unseen at the new stash house. Someone is clearly helping them. Looking at the police in her rear view mirror, she picks up her two-way radio. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="18" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1635" ElementID="48" SceneID="1634" Start="18" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="166" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1635" ElementID="190" SceneID="1634" Start="166" Length="19"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="323" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1635" ElementID="226" SceneID="1634" Start="323" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1636" ElementID="2" SceneID="1634" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>They’re there and they look ready. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good, go to the spot and wait. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Be safe ma. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="112" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="81" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. UNMARKED POLICE CAR</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> 1</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1642" ElementID="227" SceneID="1642" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1642" ElementID="104" SceneID="1642" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1642" ElementID="16" SceneID="1642" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Sitting on the corner, positioned the same as they had on the east-side stash house. Both officers have binoculars trained on the front of the house, its windows and the street and block beyond. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The familiar </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> pulls up to the block and parks in front of the house. The truck sits for a beat with no sign of movement. Then the driver’s door opens and a silhouetted lady steps from the truck. The figure walks around to the passenger’s side and reaches into the truck and grabs a red duffle bag. She’s wearing black leather gloves. The figure moves to the house. Officer #1 lifts his radio. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="368" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1644" ElementID="28" SceneID="1642" Start="368" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="285" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1644" ElementID="228" SceneID="1642" Start="285" Length="14"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="389" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1644" ElementID="201" SceneID="1642" Start="389" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>OFFICER #1 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(talking into his radio) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You guys ready back there? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="113" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="82" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. UNMARKED POLICE CAR </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">2 </Text>
      <Text>- </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1648" ElementID="229" SceneID="1648" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A second unmarked car sits in the alley behind the house. These TWO OFFICERS have their badges around their necks ready to make entry. The driver talks into the radio. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="2" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1649" ElementID="230" SceneID="1648" Start="2" Length="19"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="88" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1649" ElementID="231" SceneID="1648" Start="88" Length="19"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="161" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1649" ElementID="201" SceneID="1648" Start="161" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>OFFICER #3 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1650" ElementID="32" SceneID="1648" Start="0" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re ready. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>OFFICER #1 (O.S.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wait at the back door until you here me call for you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>OFFICER #3 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Copy that. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The two officers step from their car slow and low. Their badges catching the moon light. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="114" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="82" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">EAST</Text>
      <Text>-SIDE STASH HOUSE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Officers drive up fast. They stop in front of Cassidy’s </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>, driving up on the grass. Officer #1 has a shotgun out and ready. Officer #2 has his side arm out and ready as well. They move quickly to the front door of the house. At the front door after checking with each other, Officer #1 kicks in the door and they’re in. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="86" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1658" ElementID="28" SceneID="1657" Start="86" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="126" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1658" ElementID="29" SceneID="1657" Start="126" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="56" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1658" ElementID="104" SceneID="1657" Start="56" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="101" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1658" ElementID="232" SceneID="1657" Start="101" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="145" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1658" ElementID="233" SceneID="1657" Start="145" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="115" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="82" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">EAST</Text>
      <Text>-SIDE STASH HOUSE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1659" ElementID="198" SceneID="1659" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1659" ElementID="44" SceneID="1659" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1659" ElementID="43" SceneID="1659" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The two officers step across the threshold. Their faces look totally confused. They stand and scan the room, nothing. Nothing but the dust that was kicked up by the front door. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW-MOTION, Cassidy stands up from a hiding place behind a barricade that she has in the corner. She raises the barrel of the shotgun and shoots Officer #1 in the chest. He’s down. Officer #2 returns fire, hitting around Cassidy as she racks the shotgun, chambering another round. She fires and hits the officer in the upper chest. His gun goes flying one way and he the other. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="149" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1661" ElementID="28" SceneID="1659" Start="149" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="185" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1661" ElementID="29" SceneID="1659" Start="185" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="250" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1661" ElementID="238" SceneID="1659" Start="250" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="116" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="82" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">EAST-SIDE STASH HOUSE </Text>
      <Text>BACK STEPS - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1662" ElementID="32" SceneID="1662" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1662" ElementID="229" SceneID="1662" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1662" ElementID="239" SceneID="1662" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1662" ElementID="198" SceneID="1662" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The two other officers that are set-up on the back steps hear the gun fire and move to the door quickly, guns drawn. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="117" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="83" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">EAST-SIDE STASH HOUSE </Text>
      <Text>BACK DOOR - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1664" ElementID="229" SceneID="1664" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1664" ElementID="16" SceneID="1664" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1664" ElementID="198" SceneID="1664" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1664" ElementID="44" SceneID="1664" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1664" ElementID="43" SceneID="1664" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>IN SLOW MOTION Officer #3 kicks in the back door and the two officers enter moving in coordinated cover fashion.</Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="15" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1665" ElementID="32" SceneID="1664" Start="15" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Crouched low they move to the front room where they can see and smell gun smoke. The lead officer can hear the wounded officer in the front room moaning. Officer #3 moves slowly to the corner to peek around it to see who’s hurt. He stands to peek around the corner. Cassidy is around the other side of the corner. She slides the handgun round the corner into his chest and pulls the trigger. She spins around the corner as the officer falls back. She has the shotgun as well and bring it down, resting it on the pistol taking aim at the officer behind the fallen #3 and hits the fourth officer in the chest and he goes down. She drops the shotgun and moves back to the barricade. She gets the red duffle bag. On her way out, she steps over to the wounded officer. Standing over him she fires a single round down into him. The moaning stops. Cassidy drops the handgun next to the lifeless officer and quickly leaves the house. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="118" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="83" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">EAST</Text>
      <Text>-SIDE STASH HOUSE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1667" ElementID="13" SceneID="1667" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy comes walking out fast but not running. She jumps in the truck and starts off again fast but not crazy. Police sirens can be heard in the background. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1668" ElementID="16" SceneID="1667" Start="0" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="65" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1668" ElementID="104" SceneID="1667" Start="65" Length="5"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>SCREEN WIPE: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="119" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 1/8" Page="83" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1670" ElementID="240" SceneID="1670" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey comes strolling into the office at 10 am. The ladies are already there. They’re all gather around the couch in front of the plasma. There’s a REPORTER standing in front of the stash house. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>NEWS REPORTER </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1672" ElementID="30" SceneID="1670" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Thank you Max, stunning news here. There were four detectives shot to death inside of this house behind me. None of the police officials here would comment on camera, but I have talk to a few off camera and it looks as though it may be drug related. They say they have several solid leads that they are following. I asked if this might overlap with the FBI’s task-force just announced a few days ago. I was told that they will follow it where it leads. Back to you Max. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>POLICE OFFICERS mill around in the background of the reporter’s shot. One of the officers looks like John, one of Tara’s clients. Tara double takes. No one else takes notice of Tara’s attentions. She smiles to herself as a wave of realization washes over her. All of this is too subtle for the others to notice. She’s back on script as Shawntey moves to the TV area standing next to the couch where the ladies are sitting. Tara notices and begins to question everyone on the previous night’s events. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="101" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1674" ElementID="38" SceneID="1670" Start="101" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1675" ElementID="2" SceneID="1670" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What the hell happen? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1677" ElementID="16" SceneID="1670" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">AHHHH</Text>
      <Text>... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy just raises her shoulders. Tara gets up off the couch. She wonders over to her desk. Cassidy joins her. Shawntey and Xiomare stay on the couch. THE NEWSCASTER talks more about the slain cops and the escalating violence in the city. Cassidy and Tara definitely take notice of how they seemed to be paired up with common concerns. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>NEW CASTER AT THE DESK </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1680" ElementID="296" SceneID="1670" Start="0" Length="22"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>These detectives on top of the already mounting death toll have area civil rights activist planning protest...(fade) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>TITLES OVER BLACK SCREEN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>INMATE #</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">35728'S</Text>
      <Text> MARCO REED SR. * </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>15 DAYS TO </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>RELEASE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="120" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="84" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. BANK - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1687" ElementID="87" SceneID="1687" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1687" ElementID="212" SceneID="1687" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1687" ElementID="1" SceneID="1687" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1687" ElementID="13" SceneID="1687" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1687" ElementID="16" SceneID="1687" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1687" ElementID="198" SceneID="1687" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The black </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> that the crew does work in pulls up fast in front of the bank. Shawntey is driving with a pistol on his lap. Tara gets out of the front passenger's side her head on a swivel. Xiomare and Cassidy get out of the back. Cassidy pulls her handgun and racks the slide. Tara turns to Xiomare. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="4" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1688" ElementID="104" SceneID="1687" Start="4" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1689" ElementID="2" SceneID="1687" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wait this one out. I’m just changing a few accounts and getting </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cassidy some cash to buy more weapons. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="121" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="85" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT.  BANK </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">LOBBY </Text>
      <Text>- </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1692" ElementID="13" SceneID="1692" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1692" ElementID="16" SceneID="1692" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies enter the bank. Looking like a million bucks. They draw the attention of all in the bank. Mr. Williamson meets and shows them back to a conference room. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="101" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1693" ElementID="34" SceneID="1692" Start="101" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="122" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="85" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">BANK </Text>
      <Text>HALLWAY - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1694" ElementID="13" SceneID="1694" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1694" ElementID="16" SceneID="1694" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies follow Mr. Williamson down a hallway. He opens a door for them. The ladies enter the room. Mr. Williamson holds the door open, closing it after they enter. He walks away. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="18" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1695" ElementID="34" SceneID="1694" Start="18" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="123" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="85" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">BANK </Text>
      <Text>CONFERENCE ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>There are two briefcases on the table, both filled with bundles of hundreds. Tara and Cassidy hug. Tara hands Cassidy a envelop. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="10" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1697" ElementID="241" SceneID="1696" Start="10" Length="14"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="56" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1697" ElementID="242" SceneID="1696" Start="56" Length="19"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="118" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1697" ElementID="243" SceneID="1696" Start="118" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1698" ElementID="2" SceneID="1696" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This is the account that the rest of your cash is in. This is just walking around money to get you started. Thank you baby girl, I owe you... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>...I owe you my life. Without you believing in Marco and Me </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tara begins to tear up. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1702" ElementID="16" SceneID="1696" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Come on girl. You would do the same for me. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="124" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="85" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. BANK - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1704" ElementID="104" SceneID="1704" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1704" ElementID="90" SceneID="1704" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare is sitting in the truck in the back seat. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1706" ElementID="13" SceneID="1704" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Baby I’m going to call my mother. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You know how she be killing me about keeping the boy. I’m going to step out and fight with her. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare gets out dialing. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What up? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tomorrow dude. They nervous as hell around here. This </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> should be easy as hell. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You got a time and a place? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>She won’t tell us till the day of. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="125" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="86" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT.  </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">BANK </Text>
      <Text>LOBBY - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1718" ElementID="16" SceneID="1718" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies come back into the lobby. Tara shakes hands with Mr. Williamson. He hands her a envelop. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="89" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1719" ElementID="243" SceneID="1718" Start="89" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. WILLIAMSON </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1720" ElementID="34" SceneID="1718" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I liquidated the property and securities that you asked and transferred it all to the St. Croix accounts that you gave me. These are the receipts. We’re sorry to be losing your business. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara pulls out a catalogue envelope and hands it to Mr. Williamson. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="15" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1722" ElementID="244" SceneID="1718" Start="15" Length="20"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1723" ElementID="2" SceneID="1718" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Can you add this to your out-going mail? Thank you Mr. Williamson. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara shakes hands with Mr. Williamson then turns and leaves the bank. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="126" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="86" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. BANK - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare is still standing outside of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> on her cell with Vincent when the ladies appear. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="37" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1727" ElementID="245" SceneID="1726" Start="37" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="52" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1727" ElementID="124" SceneID="1726" Start="52" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1728" ElementID="13" SceneID="1726" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Alright ma, I got to go. I’ll call when I know I can come by. Love you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies pile in the truck, Xiomare last in. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1731" ElementID="1" SceneID="1726" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Everything was cool, right? We still rich? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1733" ElementID="2" SceneID="1726" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Everything is everything. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara notices that Shawntey is getting off a call himself. * Tara puts on her big frame sunglasses and leans back in her * seat. Shawntey pulls the truck into traffic. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="77" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1735" ElementID="246" SceneID="1726" Start="77" Length="20"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>DISSOLVE TO: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="127" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="87" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - PARKING AREA - NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Cassidy get in the Crown Vic. Cassidy is carrying a duffle bag. Cassidy tosses the bag in the back seat and gets in the driver’s seat. Xiomare jumps in Shawntey’s </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>, but no Shawntey. He comes out of the building clearly just getting off of his cell. He’s trying to put the cell away before he’s seen. Tara has taken notice. Shawntey hops in the driver’s seat of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. The car and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> pull along side each other. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1738" ElementID="16" SceneID="1737" Start="9" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="28" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1738" ElementID="247" SceneID="1737" Start="28" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="59" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1738" ElementID="157" SceneID="1737" Start="59" Length="12"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="284" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1738" ElementID="90" SceneID="1737" Start="284" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1739" ElementID="2" SceneID="1737" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wait on Ashland. If I need some back up I’ll hit you. If I do, come hard. Your radio is charged right? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1741" ElementID="1" SceneID="1737" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yep, charged them both this afternoon. If you call we’ll be right there. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara pulls away fast, followed by Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="128" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="87" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E.  UNDERGROUND PARKING GARAGE - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1744" ElementID="104" SceneID="1744" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara turns the corner and enters the underground parking. She’s driving like a bat out of hell. She circles the levels until she’s at the top floor. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>She pulls into a spot next to Mr. Diaz’s plain </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. He and * Tiny step out of their </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text> and move to the rear as they have more then a few times before. Tara steps from her truck and moves to the rear. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="30" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1746" ElementID="248" SceneID="1744" Start="30" Length="20"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1747" ElementID="8" SceneID="1744" Start="0" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What’s happening little lady. I hope you’ve been paying attention to the news. I.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy joins Tara at the rear of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUVs</Text>
      <Text> with a silenced .45 pointed at them cutting Mr. Diaz off in mid sentence. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="50" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1749" ElementID="249" SceneID="1744" Start="50" Length="12"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1750" ElementID="2" SceneID="1744" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m sorry Mr. Diaz but I’ve been paying attention. I know what the</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> you are. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="129" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="88" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E.  FBI VEHICLE - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1752" ElementID="252" SceneID="1752" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz and a FBI AGENT sit in a Crown Vic looking at the happening in front of them. The agent is taking pictures. They are looking at Shawntey leaving the office building, moving to his </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. He gets in the truck and pulls away. After Shawntey pulls away, Tara slides out of the building. She gets on her cell looking towards Shawntey driving away. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1754" ElementID="8" SceneID="1752" Start="0" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="15" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1754" ElementID="250" SceneID="1752" Start="15" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="32" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1754" ElementID="251" SceneID="1752" Start="32" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="189" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1754" ElementID="104" SceneID="1752" Start="189" Length="3"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1755" ElementID="2" SceneID="1752" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Who’s with him? What are they looking at? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">FLASHBACK ENDS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="130" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="88" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">CASSIDY WATCHES ON </Text>
      <Text>STREET - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy is looking at the car Mr. Diaz and the Agent are in through binoculars. She talks to Tara on her earpiece. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="30" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1759" ElementID="8" SceneID="1758" Start="30" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="43" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1759" ElementID="253" SceneID="1758" Start="43" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="68" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1759" ElementID="254" SceneID="1758" Start="68" Length="10"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="105" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1759" ElementID="196" SceneID="1758" Start="105" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>CLOSE ON LICENSE PLATE </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1760" ElementID="255" SceneID="1758" Start="9" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1761" ElementID="16" SceneID="1758" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t know who that is with him but that’s definitely your boy sitting in a government vehicle. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The driver is taking pictures of you now. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>END OF FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="131" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="6/8" Page="88" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. UNDERGROUND PARKING GARAGE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1765" ElementID="78" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1765" ElementID="16" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1765" ElementID="248" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1765" ElementID="104" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1765" ElementID="146" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1765" ElementID="44" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="5" ParagraphID="1765" ElementID="43" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara is standing off with Mr. Diaz and Tiny. Cassidy is holding the tool. Tiny has had enough of this </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">bullshit</Text>
      <Text>. His face contorts and he charges Cassidy. Without flinching Cassidy shoots him in the legs. Tiny goes down in a heap. Mr. Diaz reaches for Tiny then looks back to Tara. Tara looks on stone faced. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="26" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1766" ElementID="8" SceneID="1765" Start="26" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1767" ElementID="2" SceneID="1765" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Who’d you give up. You wearing a wire right now? (a beat) No worries RICO! That’s your name right? I got people too, sir! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(looks at Cassidy) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let’s put this garbage in the car and go. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz lefts out a belly laugh. Tiny sits on the ground in pain. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’ll see Reed. You and that </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">nigga</Text>
      <Text> of yours think you’re smart huh? I’ll be to see you both. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea, yea, yea. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara gives Cassidy a head nod and she approaches Mr. Diaz and pats him down taking a little Derringer two shot .22 caliber gun off of him. Tiny has a .44 Magnum in his waistband. Cassidy moves back to the car and grabs a roll of grey duck tape. She pulls the tape and moves towards Tiny and Mr. Diaz. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="92" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1776" ElementID="256" SceneID="1765" Start="92" Length="22"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="219" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1776" ElementID="257" SceneID="1765" Start="219" Length="24"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="132" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="89" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY WAITS ON </Text>
      <Text>WOODWARD AVENUE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey sits in the driver’s seat. Xiomare is in the back seat not pressed at all. Shawntey looks as though he’s holding on to something too tight. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1778" ElementID="1" SceneID="1777" Start="0" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="36" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1778" ElementID="13" SceneID="1777" Start="36" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON XIOMARE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare is looking at her cell </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">texting</Text>
      <Text> about the impending happenings. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="26" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1780" ElementID="90" SceneID="1777" Start="26" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="133" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="89" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. UNDERGROUND PARKING GARAGE -</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps"> NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="7" ParagraphID="1781" ElementID="45" SceneID="1781" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1781" ElementID="257" SceneID="1781" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1781" ElementID="248" SceneID="1781" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1781" ElementID="104" SceneID="1781" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy is shoving the torso of Tiny into the back seat of their car. The task has Cassidy totally winded. Tiny is still in pain from the gunshot to the leg. Tara on the other side of the car bends down to talk to Mr. Diaz in the back seat through his window. Both he and Tiny have grey duck tape around their wrists, mouths, and ankles. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="214" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1782" ElementID="8" SceneID="1781" Start="214" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1782" ElementID="16" SceneID="1781" Start="0" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="32" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1782" ElementID="78" SceneID="1781" Start="32" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1783" ElementID="2" SceneID="1781" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Thought you serve us up, (a beat) I got you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(muffled) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>YOU DEAD BITCH. YOU DEAD BITCH! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara smiles at Mr. Diaz then gives him an air kiss. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’ll see you when I see you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(to Cassidy) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let’s go. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara and Cassidy walk to Mr. Diaz’s. Tara hops in the driver’s seat of the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>THE SHOT floats along the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>, at the rear under the bumper a black box with a flashing red light can be seen. A tracing device. Mr. Diaz is nothing if he’s not thorough. Cassidy and Tara pull out of the parking spot, fast. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="113" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1794" ElementID="258" SceneID="1781" Start="113" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="134" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1" Page="90" Title=""/>
      <Text>I/E. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">SHAWNTEY WAITS ON </Text>
      <Text>WOODWARD AVENUE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1795" ElementID="16" SceneID="1795" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1795" ElementID="104" SceneID="1795" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1795" ElementID="212" SceneID="1795" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey is looking anxious. Xiomare is cool waiting for the next move. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1797" ElementID="1" SceneID="1795" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Something ain’t right, It’s taking to long. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1799" ElementID="13" SceneID="1795" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Chill big man, if it was a problem she would have called us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(picking her nails) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Naw</Text>
      <Text>, man I think something... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (ON THE TWO-WAY CELL) </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1804" ElementID="2" SceneID="1795" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We’re pulling around now. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>See. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara pulls up on Ashland Ave facing the opposite direction of Shawntey. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">How’d</Text>
      <Text> it go. I was getting worried? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Everything is everything. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where’s the car? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Oh </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">ahh</Text>
      <Text>... Mr. Diaz got tied up with it. So we left it with him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy starts to chuckle in the background. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Follow me. We’re back at the office. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara pulls off fast. Shawntey makes a U-turn and follows. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="135" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 7/8" Page="91" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - PARKING AREA - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1822" ElementID="42" SceneID="1822" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1822" ElementID="16" SceneID="1822" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1822" ElementID="291" SceneID="1822" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The vehicles driven by Tara and Shawntey pull up into the parking lot. They all step from the cars. Shawntey is slow to leave his seat. The ladies all hug each other in front of the cars, a group hug. Shawntey watches looking through the front windshield. The action slows to SLOW-MOTION the ladies caught in their embrace. Tara looks up at Shawntey with the stink-eye. Shawntey notices the look and is confused by it. Just as he catches the look he turns to look over his shoulder to see a white cargo van pulling up on them fast. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1823" ElementID="2" SceneID="1822" Start="0" Length="27"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The action returns to real time, the van stops and the side door slides open. Three masked men step from the van, all holding assault weapons. Shawntey eases from the driver’s seat facing the masked men. One of the masked men steps forward. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="33" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1824" ElementID="288" SceneID="1822" Start="33" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="78" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1824" ElementID="289" SceneID="1822" Start="78" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="126" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1824" ElementID="290" SceneID="1822" Start="126" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MASKED MAN #1 </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1825" ElementID="35" SceneID="1822" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Keys. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The ladies look at each other, then over at Shawntey. Cassidy standing at the back of the group of ladies, starts to ease her hand to her back where she has the silenced gun from her earlier business. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1828" ElementID="1" SceneID="1822" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Cassidy please.... Tara just give them what they want so we can live through this. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1830" ElementID="13" SceneID="1822" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea give them what they want. What </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">we</Text>
      <Text> want. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare steps towards the gunmen and turns back to Tara. Tara raises an eyebrow, not surprised but disappointed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>XIOMARE JAMES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I know a sharp business woman like yourself can see a deal that you just can’t pass up. Great business move I think, I just went from 1 of </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>5 to a 50-50 partner. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(interrupting) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">CIO</Text>
      <Text>, what the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> are you doing? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">XIOMARE</Text>
      <Text> JAMES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Shawntey</Text>
      <Text> you should’ve grew a pair </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>of balls big guy. This was your move to make. You was in the same meetings as me. I guess that’s the difference between 1st place and last place. Holding on to some brother </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text> with some </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">nigga</Text>
      <Text> that passed you over. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy looks to Shawntey, looking at him like he has </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucked</Text>
      <Text> up bad. Tara looks at Shawntey then back at the masked men. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MASKED MAN #1 </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>KEYS! Not going to say it again. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare with her back to the masked men is shocked when the gunman comes over behind her and kicks her back towards Tara. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MASKED MAN #1 (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Vincent has a NEW deal for you too! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Xiomare turns to the gunman shocked to hear this. The gunman shoots Xiomare in the chest. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara, Shawntey and Cassidy take a step back. Tara tosses the keys to the lead masked man. He grabs the them out of the air and quickly moves to the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">SUV</Text>
      <Text>. He starts it and pulls off. The remaining gunmen slowly move back to the van, one jumps in. The other stands in front of the van’s sliding door. He pulls the slide on his assault rifle. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Shawntey looks to Tara they both know what’s coming. Their look is in SLOW-MOTION. Tara has a look of peace. Shawntey looks panicked. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SHAWNTEY ROSS </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>TARA,... I! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The gunman let’s out a blast of gun fire hitting Cassidy, Shawntey and Tara. After he finishes firing, the masked man gets in the van and pulls away fast. Tara is laid out with the dead eyes. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>TITLES OVER BLACK SCREEN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>INMATE #</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">35728'S</Text>
      <Text> MARCO REED SR. * </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>RELEASE DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="136" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="92" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. PRISON - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1859" ElementID="5" SceneID="1859" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco walks out of the gates. He pauses, looks around, breathing in the air of freedom. He looks around, his mind coming back to the now. His face starts to contour. He’s getting out to nothing, to no one. An unmarked police car pulls up fast right in front of him. A MAN hops out. He has his badge in his hand. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="209" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1860" ElementID="190" SceneID="1859" Start="209" Length="19"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SPECIAL AGENT COLLINS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1861" ElementID="36" SceneID="1859" Start="0" Length="21"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Marco Reed, Special Agent Collins, come with us. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The man opens the back door of the car. Marco slowly gets in. The car pulls away as fast as it landed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>END OF FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="137" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="93" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. FBI TASK-FORCE OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1865" ElementID="58" SceneID="1865" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1865" ElementID="3" SceneID="1865" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1865" ElementID="4" SceneID="1865" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>Present </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Back in the present, Marco sits in the chair, the office back to life from the frozen moment that began all this. Marco fields the questions as they are fired at him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1868" ElementID="5" SceneID="1865" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>All I know is she had been writing me these letters about how this Shawntey guy had hi-jacked her entire business. She wrote about not being able to go to the cops, because they were threatening my son and mother-in-law. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>SPECIAL AGENT COLLINS </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1870" ElementID="36" SceneID="1865" Start="0" Length="21"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Let me see the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> letters. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco slowly pulls the letters from his pocket and they are instantly snatched up. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="138" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="93" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. PRISON CELL - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>After Marco tapes up the picture of Tara and Marco Jr. He reads a short part of a letter, It Reads: </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="45" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1875" ElementID="7" SceneID="1873" Start="45" Length="9"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="25" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1875" ElementID="287" SceneID="1873" Start="25" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Dear Marco, </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>This has been a terrible time. I know Shawntey was your partner but he’s totally changed. The office girl Xiomare is frighten to death of him and his friends. I think they are dealing drugs or something bad because they keep weird hours and stay intoxicated.... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>After reading this small portion, Marco puts the letter in a stack of others. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>END OF FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="139" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="94" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. FBI TASK-FORCE OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The agents are standing around Marco reading these letters. Marco is cool, not pressed or nervous. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="51" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1881" ElementID="286" SceneID="1880" Start="51" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1882" ElementID="5" SceneID="1880" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Officers, I did my time, my wife is missing and I haven’t held my son in five years. I just want to go home to my boy. This has nothing to do with me. I don’t know what’s going on. I just want to get on with my life. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="140" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="94" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. PRISON VISITOR’S ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco sits down at the visitor’s window, he picks up the phone. We can’t see the other person that is visiting Marco. Just his big black onyx ring on his pinky finger defines him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1887" ElementID="5" SceneID="1884" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>If you don’t know about him, then how do we play it? Brother or not make sure of everybody! Look out for her. Make sure she stays on the path and can bare the pressure. She doesn’t know if she can do it but I know when she decides to do something, it’s done. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>John gets up and walks to the door. He gives a head nod to the CORRECTIONS GUARD on Marco’s side of the glass. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1889" ElementID="38" SceneID="1884" Start="0" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON JOHN’S HAND He slips a couple of hundreds to the Corrections Guard that he passes on the way out. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="30" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1890" ElementID="284" SceneID="1884" Start="30" Length="20"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="58" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1890" ElementID="285" SceneID="1884" Start="58" Length="17"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="">FLASHBACK ENDS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="141" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="94" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. FBI TASK-FORCE OFFICE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco looks up, around at the faces of the agents. He hears no resistant. He stands to his feet. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1894" ElementID="5" SceneID="1892" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Now if I’m not under arrest, I’m leaving. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco looks around at the faces of the agents. In the back he can see John. His badge is around his neck. He’s twisting his onyx pinky ring. Marco doesn’t acknowledge him but John gives him a quick wink. Marco has pulled it off and John salutes him. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="70" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1896" ElementID="38" SceneID="1892" Start="70" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="80" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1896" ElementID="283" SceneID="1892" Start="80" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="124" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1896" ElementID="65" SceneID="1892" Start="124" Length="15"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>OVER BLACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (V.O.) (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(whispers) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>One more. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="142" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="95" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. WAREHOUSE DISTRICT - ABANDON WAREHOUSE BUILDING - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>TEN HISPANIC MEN run towards the building. Mr. Diaz and Tiny look on, watching the hit squad closing in. In Mr. Diaz’s he holds a radio receiver. It’s getting a strong signal from the transmitter from his car truck. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="43" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1903" ElementID="8" SceneID="1902" Start="43" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1903" ElementID="281" SceneID="1902" Start="0" Length="16"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="56" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1903" ElementID="282" SceneID="1902" Start="56" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="128" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1903" ElementID="91" SceneID="1902" Start="128" Length="16"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="143" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="95" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. WAREHOUSE DISTRICT - ABANDON WAREHOUSE BUILDING - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="4" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1904" ElementID="275" SceneID="1904" Start="4" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1904" ElementID="280" SceneID="1904" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The transmitter still is sending a signal. A hand comes in and pulls the box from it’s place. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>ONE OF VINCENT’S MEN looks at it for a beat, seeing the red light blinking. He holds it up and yells over to the office where MEN are cutting drugs and sitting around talking </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">shit</Text>
      <Text>. Vincent is among them. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="181" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1906" ElementID="23" SceneID="1904" Start="181" Length="7"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1906" ElementID="278" SceneID="1904" Start="0" Length="20"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="126" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1906" ElementID="279" SceneID="1904" Start="126" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>VINCENT’S MAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1907" ElementID="37" SceneID="1904" Start="0" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> is this thing? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="144" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="95" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. WAREHOUSE DISTRICT - ABANDON WAREHOUSE BUILDING - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">NIGHT</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1909" ElementID="276" SceneID="1909" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tiny and Mr. Diaz are still watching as suddenly ten marked police cars pull up fast to the warehouse. Several SWAT unit trucks pull up as well. All the POLICE come out of their vehicles with their weapons ready. The SWAT GUYS lead the group of officers into the building. Tiny and Mr. Diaz look confused at the happenings. Without taking his eyes off of the police. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1910" ElementID="8" SceneID="1909" Start="9" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1910" ElementID="78" SceneID="1909" Start="0" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="217" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1910" ElementID="277" SceneID="1909" Start="217" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>What the hell? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>He looks up to Tiny, then back to the police. The police have assembled and are making entry into the warehouse. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let’s get the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> out of here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz spins on his heels and moves away from the scene. Tiny joins him, looking back to the police as he moves away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="145" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 2/8" Page="96" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. DARK SIDE STREET</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">/MR. DIAZ PARKING SPOT</Text>
      <Text> - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1917" ElementID="274" SceneID="1917" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz and Tiny come from their hiding place onto the side street that they have parked their car for the quiet get away. When they arrive at the car, police cars pull up fast from all directions. The police and their lights bring the street to life. Mr. Diaz looks confused, not sure what this is. POLICE jump out of their cars and cuff Mr. Diaz and Tiny. An unseen man walks up to them. Mr Diaz looks to the man. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1918" ElementID="8" SceneID="1917" Start="0" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good you look like you’re in</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style=""> </Text>
      <Text>charge. What the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> is going on? What are we being arrested for? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The unseen man is smoking a cigarette. He flicks the butt away showing the onyx pinky ring. John moves to Mr. Diaz’s car. He reaches in and pulls out the radio receiver that Mr. Diaz used to track down his truck with the drugs inside. John then walks it back over to Mr. Diaz and Tiny. He holds it up in front of Mr. Diaz. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="75" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1921" ElementID="180" SceneID="1917" Start="75" Length="15"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="154" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1921" ElementID="275" SceneID="1917" Start="154" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s nothing. I have a dog with a radio collar. Who the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fuck</Text>
      <Text> are you? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>JOHN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1924" ElementID="38" SceneID="1917" Start="0" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m Sergeant </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Hairston</Text>
      <Text>, Metro </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Narcotics. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Drugs, I don’t know anything about </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">drugs</Text>
      <Text>. I’m a business man. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>John reaches into his pocket and pulls out the cell that he gave Tara. He holds it up to show him. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="47" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1930" ElementID="90" SceneID="1917" Start="47" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>JOHN </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Oh yea, we’ll see won’t we. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.50" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(turns to uniformed officers) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Take them. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Mr. Diaz yells at John as he is dragged away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MR. DIAZ </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Call the FBI, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">Hairston</Text>
      <Text> call the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucking</Text>
      <Text> FBI. I’m working with them. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I work for the FBI... Look that bitch that gave you that phone is the one. She runs the whole thing </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>(</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fades</Text>
      <Text>) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>He keeps yelling behind the door of the police car when he’s put inside. Mr. Diaz is throwing everything at him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="146" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="6/8" Page="97" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. TORRES HOUSE - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1943" ElementID="7" SceneID="1943" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1943" ElementID="131" SceneID="1943" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco gets out of a cab in front of his mother-in-law's house. Little Marco comes running out and jumps in his father's arms. Marco Sr closes his eyes and hugs his son with all his soul. Marco makes his way to the door. Ms. Torres stands in the door, arms cross looking not very happy to see him. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="220" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1944" ElementID="20" SceneID="1943" Start="220" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MS. TORRES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>If it was up to me, no way would I do this. But I promised her that when it came time, I would. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>She reaches down and hands him that same catalogue envelope that Tara asked Mr. Williamson to mail and little MARCO's suitcase. Marco looks back up to his mother-in-law, tears in his eyes. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="41" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1947" ElementID="273" SceneID="1943" Start="41" Length="18"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MS. TORRES (CONT’D) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Promise me something? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1950" ElementID="5" SceneID="1943" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Anything. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MS. TORRES </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No more. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I promise! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Ms. Torres gives Marco a heart felt head nod, though she doesn’t reach out to him physically. Marco gives her a nod back then turns and he and Marco Jr move back to the awaiting cab. Marco looks back to Ms. Torres, she recrosses her arms again none to happy. Marco ducks in and the cab pulls away slowly. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="147" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="98" Title=""/>
      <Text>INT. CAB - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1957" ElementID="7" SceneID="1957" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1957" ElementID="5" SceneID="1957" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1957" ElementID="267" SceneID="1957" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1957" ElementID="266" SceneID="1957" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Riding in the back of the cab. Marco Sr looks to his son who smiles back at him. Marco Sr opens the envelope. A bundle of hundreds, a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">iphone</Text>
      <Text>, bank account information and two passports slide out. Marco looks back to his son, then out at the world whipping by in the cab’s window as they roll to the airport. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="100" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1958" ElementID="268" SceneID="1957" Start="100" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="112" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1958" ElementID="269" SceneID="1957" Start="112" Length="18"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="132" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1958" ElementID="270" SceneID="1957" Start="132" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="142" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1958" ElementID="271" SceneID="1957" Start="142" Length="24"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="171" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1958" ElementID="272" SceneID="1957" Start="171" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="148" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="98" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. LAX AIRPORT - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1959" ElementID="5" SceneID="1959" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The cab pulls up in front of the airport. Marco and his son get out and walk into the airport, still only carrying Marco Jr’s small suitcase. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="42" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1960" ElementID="7" SceneID="1959" Start="42" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="4" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1960" ElementID="266" SceneID="1959" Start="4" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="126" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1960" ElementID="131" SceneID="1959" Start="126" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="149" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="98" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT.  BANK OF ST. CROIX  - DAY </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1962" ElementID="5" SceneID="1962" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco Sr comes strolling out of the bank with a briefcase, wearing a tropical print shirt and flip-flops. He looks happy, unburdened. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1963" ElementID="7" SceneID="1962" Start="0" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="46" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1963" ElementID="261" SceneID="1962" Start="46" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="67" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1963" ElementID="262" SceneID="1962" Start="67" Length="22"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="94" CategoryID="6" ParagraphID="1963" ElementID="263" SceneID="1962" Start="94" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>A smile spreads across his face as he puts on his sunglasses. Marco Jr sits on the moped that they rode to the bank. He’s eating a huge tropical frozen treat. Marco Sr frowns and pulls off his glasses. Marco Jr points to a lady with her back to them. She’s standing at the mobile street vendor. The lady turns and it’s Tara. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="83" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1964" ElementID="236" SceneID="1962" Start="83" Length="5"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="319" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1964" ElementID="2" SceneID="1962" Start="319" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="136" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1964" ElementID="264" SceneID="1962" Start="136" Length="21"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="50" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1964" ElementID="265" SceneID="1962" Start="50" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="150" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="98" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">CASSIDY PULLS OVER ON </Text>
      <Text>STREET - NIGHT </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>FLASHBACK </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The SUV pulls to the curb. Cassidy and Tara both hop out of the truck. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="4" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1967" ElementID="104" SceneID="1965" Start="4" Length="3"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="27" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1967" ElementID="16" SceneID="1965" Start="27" Length="7"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON DUFFLE BAG Cassidy’s hand reaches in the duffle bag and pulls out a bullet resistant vest and tosses it to Tara. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="50" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1968" ElementID="260" SceneID="1965" Start="50" Length="10"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Cassidy starts to pull off her jacket to put the vest on under her clothes. They both duck back into the car once they have them on. Tara picks up the radio. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1970" ElementID="2" SceneID="1965" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Everything is cool, we’re pulling around now. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="151" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="98" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. REED HOLDINGS INC. OFFICE - PARKING AREA - NIGHT </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1972" ElementID="1" SceneID="1972" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1972" ElementID="13" SceneID="1972" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1972" ElementID="46" SceneID="1972" Start="0" Length="0"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1972" ElementID="259" SceneID="1972" Start="0" Length="0"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON TARA’S EYE Suddenly she blinks. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara climbs to her feet. She looks over to Cassidy. She’s bleeding. Tara gets up and runs over to her. Cassidy stirs, sitting up as well. Her arm is bleeding. Tara helps Cassidy to her feet. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>CASSIDY REDMAN </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1975" ElementID="16" SceneID="1972" Start="0" Length="14"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Of course the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucker</Text>
      <Text> didn’t hit the damn vest. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>TARA REED </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1977" ElementID="2" SceneID="1972" Start="0" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good thing they didn’t shoot us in the head. That </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">woud</Text>
      <Text> have been </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="">fucked</Text>
      <Text>. Let’s get out of here. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Tara helps Cassidy to the car. When they get to the car Tara walks Cassidy around to the passenger’s side and helps her inside the car. Once she has Cassidy in the car Tara runs around to the driver’s side. She stops when she circles behind the car to look at Shawntey and Xiomare’s bodies. After a beat of taking it in she continues to the driver’s side. She hops in the car.  The car reverses out of the parking spot then pulls away fast. The crime scene is that of blood, gun shells, and dead bodies. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="26" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1979" ElementID="48" SceneID="1972" Start="26" Length="3"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="152" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="99" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. BANK OF ST. CROIX - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON MARCO SR. He has a big smile on his face. He has won, beaten them all and emerged with his family. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1981" ElementID="5" SceneID="1980" Start="9" Length="8"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco Sr joins his family at the mopeds. He kisses both Tara and Marco Jr before he secures the briefcase in the basket on the back of his scooter. He gets on with Jr and they ride off. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="33" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1982" ElementID="236" SceneID="1980" Start="33" Length="6"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="65" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1982" ElementID="237" SceneID="1980" Start="65" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="96" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1982" ElementID="106" SceneID="1980" Start="96" Length="9"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR. (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tara has touched them all. She’s as tough as nails. Thank God I’m on her side.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="153" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="99" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. ST. CROIX ROAD. - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="1" Size="12" Style="AllCaps">DAY</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>VERY HIGH ANGLE </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>Marco Sr and Jr and Tara ride down a long straight road. The sun is setting, a warm and inviting vision. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="0" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1987" ElementID="5" SceneID="1985" Start="0" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="13" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1987" ElementID="7" SceneID="1985" Start="13" Length="2"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="20" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1987" ElementID="2" SceneID="1985" Start="20" Length="4"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="25" CategoryID="3" ParagraphID="1987" ElementID="236" SceneID="1985" Start="25" Length="4"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.25" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character">
      <Text>MARCO REED SR (V.O.) </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="6.00" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I honor this new life that we’ve made. And just like momma Torres ask. There will be no more! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>THE END </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Transition">
      <Text>FADE TO BLACK. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="154" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="100" Title=""/>
      <Text>EXT. ST. CROIX STREET - DAY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE ON A PICTURE OF TARA. The picture is handed from one hand to another. </Text>
    <UserParagraphData><TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="9" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1993" ElementID="235" SceneID="1992" Start="9" Length="17"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>The picture is handed to a street vendor of frozen treats. The same man that sold the Reed family their treats. The vendor hands the picture back to Mr. Diaz. He has a big cigar in his mouth. The street vendor shakes his head yes. </Text>
      <UserParagraphData>
        
      <TaggerParagraphData xmlns="http://www.finaldraft.com/ns/Tagger"><TaggerElementInstance Offset="149" CategoryID="0" ParagraphID="1994" ElementID="8" SceneID="1992" Start="149" Length="8"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="166" CategoryID="4" ParagraphID="1994" ElementID="129" SceneID="1992" Start="166" Length="11"/><TaggerElementInstance Offset="196" CategoryID="1" ParagraphID="1994" ElementID="234" SceneID="1992" Start="196" Length="13"/></TaggerParagraphData></UserParagraphData>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="7.10" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition">
      <Text>CUT TO BLACK: </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Full" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.50" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action">
      <Text>END CREDITS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
  </Content>

